  '[{"text":"Send feedback regarding missing pages in sitemap to Colin for alignment (42:53)","completed":false},{"text":"Bring up account record CSV and Mulesoft integration status during GPS team meeting (30:55)","completed":false},{"text":"Present the data fields to GPS team for mapping and confirm their approach including masking needs for compliance (39:15)","completed":false},{"text":"Rework brochure designs into a tree hierarchy showing cross-sell opportunities and combine consumer and business content as feasible, adjusting layout to horizontal for better spacing (21:34)","completed":false},{"text":"Revise postcard layout with copy redistribution to front and ensure postal compliance regarding stamp and address placement (33:13)","completed":false},{"text":"Update brand guidelines and assets with new font choice (32:32)","completed":false},{"text":"Schedule and lead GPS meeting to confirm API and Mulesoft development status and timelines (40:56)","completed":false},{"text":"Finalize email template designs after stakeholder approval (39:54)","completed":false},{"text":"Coordinate with printing vendors for postcard needs considering compliance feedback (33:13)","completed":false},{"text":"Provide final feedback on brochure and postcard content emphasizing compliance, simplicity, and usability for retail staff (22:04)","completed":false},{"text":"Review product page content during copy editing phase and update as new products (e.g., Zelle) launch (42:53)","completed":false},{"text":"Participate in leading GPS meeting to set clear responsibilities, timelines, and deliverables (39:54)","completed":false},{"text":"Lead social media setup and training sessions once Jane returns; arrange for test campaign execution (43:33)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
