ting of sample test records in sandbox environment (26:40)","completed":false},{"text":"Share the latest version of the Excel field mapping spreadsheet with Gabriel and the team immediately after the meeting (53:20)","completed":false},{"text":"Provide HubSpot API & developer documentation links to Gabriel for integration preparation (56:50)","completed":false},{"text":"Build sandbox environment incorporating agreed field mappings for Salesforce-HubSpot-MuleSoft syncs (52:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Coordinate sharing of sample CSV test data for integration testing (52:15)","completed":false},{"text":"Develop clear timeline chart of deliverables and deadlines related to integrations and marketing streams for communication to wider team (55:30)","completed":false},{"text":"Assist Victor and Christina with ongoing data review and validation tasks (30:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Support discussions on householding strategy and ensure graduated roll-out with communications to marketing and sales (23:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Advise on sensitive field exclusions in data sync (gender identity etc.) for legal compliance (20:45)","completed":false},{"text":"Coordinate team meetings with Cash Management and Prosper product SMEs for API integration discussions (36:45)","completed":false},{"text":"Provide list of Encompass fields being currently integrated to assist marketing prioritization (47:50)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
