-- Meeting: KTC // MiD: Weekly Marketing Meeting (2025-12-23 18:00:00+00)
WITH new_meeting AS (
  INSERT INTO compass_meetings (contract_id, meeting_date, source, external_id, title, participants, duration_seconds, recording_url, transcript, sentiment, raw_metadata, created_at, updated_at)
  VALUES (
    '72cdc11e-fd4f-4d90-8688-1fc1484de2b0',
    '2025-12-23 18:00:00+00',
    'fireflies',
    '01KCMJGQH85T45QFRTS6R3ZQVC',
    'KTC // MiD: Weekly Marketing Meeting',
    '{"Colin Costigan","Colin Costigan","Michael Kersten","Kristen Baller"}'::text[],
    1704,
    'https://us02web.zoom.us/j/83519004309?pwd=JvKSZR6BzSlyNxK5WTgZHYayMsLSKi.1',
    '{"id":"01KCMJGQH85T45QFRTS6R3ZQVC","title":"KTC // MiD: Weekly Marketing Meeting","summary":{"notes":"## **Account-Based Marketing (ABM) Strategy and Outbound Campaign**\n\nThe team agreed on launching a focused ABM campaign targeting private equity (PE) operating partners and portfolio company leaders to build a predictable pipeline beyond referrals.\n\n- **Colin Costigan** presented a detailed **30+ page ABM plan** emphasizing a narrow focus on PE operators and portfolio companies to turn KTC’s referral momentum into a consistent pipeline (07:00)  \n    - The strategy layers email sequences, LinkedIn outreach, retargeted ads, and podcast content to build brand awareness and top-of-mind recall for hiring needs.  \n    - The campaign aims for quality engagement over volume, starting with **four emails** and refining weekly based on open rates and website visits, avoiding a fixed email count upfront.  \n    - Paid ads are included with a recommended starting budget of **$3,000**, to be regularly reviewed and adjusted based on performance metrics.  \n    - This multi-touch approach is designed to keep KTC visible until prospects are ready to engage actively.  \n\n- **Michael Kersten** raised interest in integrating contact data and CRM workflows with tools like **Clay** and HubSpot to improve outbound efficiency (09:30)  \n    - Colin confirmed the team will help broker Clay access due to recent changes from self-serve to rep-driven sales, addressing Michael’s difficulty getting direct support.  \n    - The integration will support clean data flow and allow tracking of leads alongside HubSpot records, enabling marketing and sales alignment.  \n    - Colin explained they will build a **custom dashboard (\"data box\")** linking campaign metrics, HubSpot data, and website activity for transparent, real-time tracking accessible by KTC (24:30).  \n    - This dashboard will include engagement signals to guide timely outreach, such as website visit frequency and email interactions.  \n\n## **Website Development and SEO Optimization**\n\nThe website redesign is progressing with multiple pages designed and content rewritten to improve keyword rankings and support the ABM strategy.\n\n- The team reviewed pages including **Executive, Resources, Contingent Hiring, and Services**, all integrated into a feedback tool called **Markup** for easy commenting and edits (12:20)  \n    - Michael emphasized the importance of highlighting both **contingent and retained search** terms to improve search engine visibility for common client queries (13:00).  \n    - Colin confirmed SEO is a key focus in the new content, aiming to maintain and enhance current keyword rankings without losing momentum.  \n    - A keyword table outlining targeted phrases per page will be shared for transparency and approval.  \n\n- Logo and branding updates are underway based on feedback to increase green tones and explore gradient effects while preserving a professional look (19:20)  \n    - Michael suggested subtle color blends to align with parent company **Richie May** branding for future integration, aiming for seamless visual cohesion by Q1 or Q2 2024.  \n    - Colin confirmed the team will prepare logo versions reflecting potential co-branding as an RM Talent Solutions affiliate, ready for deployment when needed (21:40).  \n    - Email signatures, letterhead, and other collateral will be updated accordingly after final logo approval.  \n\n## **Content Marketing and Podcast Development**\n\nA structured content calendar and podcast framework will drive thought leadership and client engagement using internal and external guests.\n\n- Colin shared a **living content calendar** with Michael and Kristen to track topics, guests, publish dates, and URLs, allowing dynamic collaboration and updates (14:00)  \n    - Michael confirmed **Darren Pitre, EVP Sales at Sunbelt Solomon**, is ready to participate as a guest, signaling early content momentum.  \n    - The team will provide guests with a flexible framework and talking points to simplify participation and maintain consistent messaging.  \n\n- Michael proposed leveraging high-energy external voices like **Felicia, CMO of Richie May**, and potential interviews with **Alex (PE firm principal)** and placed CROs to diversify content and testimonials (16:00)  \n    - Colin agreed to build interview frameworks and research guest backgrounds to maximize relevance and audience interest.  \n    - Some interviews may be recorded in Q1 2024 depending on availability, supporting a staggered content rollout aligned with the website launch and campaign schedules.  \n\n- Kristen emphasized the importance of scheduling and deadline management to ensure content production aligns with Q1 goals and avoids delays (18:20).  \n\n## **Operational and Technical Integrations**\n\nThe team is aligning systems and workflows to support marketing automation, tracking, and domain management for a smooth launch and ongoing operations.\n\n- Michael noted the need for seamless **HubSpot integration and dashboard setup** to monitor campaigns and manage leads, with Colin confirming their ability to develop and maintain this infrastructure (24:00)  \n    - The HubSpot dashboard will enable both internal and client-side visibility into lead flow and campaign effectiveness.  \n\n- Domain and email management will transition to KTC branding, with **Google account admin access** handed over to the marketing team for control and alignment (27:40)  \n    - Michael assigned Brian, the Google admin, to coordinate this transition without disrupting existing domains or email services.  \n    - Colin stressed the preference for full admin control to streamline future changes and reduce dependencies.  \n\n- Meeting cadence was confirmed to resume on **January 6th**, with flexibility around Michael’s travel in mid-January, ensuring timely reviews of content and website progress (26:30).  \n\n## **Strategic Market Positioning and Future Planning**\n\nThe overall strategy focuses on evolving KTC from a referral-based firm to a data-driven, visible market leader in PE search, with layered content and branding supporting long-term growth.\n\n- Colin framed the ABM plan as a way to shift from unpredictable referrals to a controlled, repeatable pipeline driven by targeted multi-channel contact (07:10)  \n    - This approach positions KTC as a **“senior speed first” alternative** to competitors like Korn Ferry, focusing on rapid, clear hiring processes.  \n    - The plan emphasizes consistent brand exposure across channels to become the default option when clients decide to hire.  \n\n- Michael highlighted the need for brand cohesion with Richie May to prepare for future integration without disrupting current identity, reflecting a phased approach to corporate alignment (20:50)  \n    - This foresight aims to reduce friction and maintain client confidence during eventual co-branding or acquisition transitions.  \n\n- The content strategy, including podcasts and guest interviews, supports thought leadership and client engagement, helping differentiate KTC in a competitive market (16:20)  \n    - By using client testimonials and expert voices, KTC plans to build trust and showcase unique value propositions.  \n\n- Kristen’s focus on deadlines and scheduling reinforces the importance of execution discipline to realize strategic goals within Q1 2024.","outline":null,"keywords":["Account-Based Marketing","Website Development","Content Calendar","Paid Advertising","Lead Data Integration","Branding Strategy"],"overview":"- **Launch of ABM Campaign:** Focus on private equity leaders to create a predictable pipeline using emails, ads, and podcasts.  \n- **Integration with CRM:** Enhance efficiency through Clay and HubSpot integration to improve lead tracking and data flow.  \n- **Website Redesign Progress:** Multiple pages are being developed with SEO focus to boost keyword rankings and support ABM.  \n- **Content Calendar Establishment:** Structured plan to include guest interviews and maintain engagement aligned with launch strategies.  \n- **Branding Updates:** Logo redesign incorporating green tones and co-branding with Richie May to ensure cohesive identity.  \n- **Operational Workflow Alignment:** HubSpot dashboard and domain management will facilitate campaign monitoring and secure brand transition.","action_items":"\n**Colin Costigan**\nShare the detailed ABM plan document and provide access to Markup tool for website feedback (07:16)\nContact Clay representative to facilitate Michael Kersten’s Clay subscription acquisition and resolve lack of direct support (10:55)\nDevelop a data dashboard (“data box”) linked with HubSpot for exportable front-of-funnel marketing performance metrics, accessible via Pulse portal (24:30)\n\n**Marketing Team**\nContinue developing and refining the website content, focusing on SEO keywords including ''contingent'' and ''retained'' hiring terms (12:50)\nProduce various logo iterations incorporating more green and potential Richie May co-branded versions, including email signature and letterhead templates (19:45)\n\n**Michael Kersten**\nProvide LinkedIn profiles for potential podcast guests such as Darren Pitre, Felicia (CMO Richie May), Alex (F3 Principal), and Randy (CRO EMC) to aid framework and research for interviews (17:10)\nCoordinate with Brian (Google admin) on transitioning staff emails to KTC Search domain, then hand over control to marketing for environment management (27:45)\n\n**Kristen Baller**\nCoordinate a one-on-one for scheduling content recordings and establishing deadlines (18:25)\n\n**All participants**\nPrepare for January 6th meeting and adjust schedules around Michael’s travel on January 14-16, keeping January 13th meeting slot confirmed (26:30)\n"},"duration":28.399999618530273,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Colin Costigan"},{"id":1,"name":"Colin Costigan"},{"id":2,"name":"Michael Kersten"},{"id":3,"name":"Kristen Baller"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Foreign.","index":0,"end_time":204.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":204.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Hey, how''s it going?","index":1,"end_time":212.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":211.76,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Good.","index":2,"end_time":213.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":212.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"How are you doing?","index":3,"end_time":214.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":213.08,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right.","index":4,"end_time":214.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":214.24,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Got any holiday plans?","index":5,"end_time":218.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":216.88,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, I had a shitload of work to catch up on, so that''s about what I''m doing.","index":6,"end_time":223.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":219.92,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Well, at least.","index":7,"end_time":225.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":224.72,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"At least some of the world is slowing down and then you can catch up, right?","index":8,"end_time":229.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":225.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s.","index":9,"end_time":230.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":229.68,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"That''s the plan.","index":10,"end_time":231.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":230.4,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Hopefully it stays.","index":11,"end_time":232.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":231.12,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Stays to.","index":12,"end_time":233.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":232.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"To that plan.","index":13,"end_time":234.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":233.6,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah, totally.","index":14,"end_time":235.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":234.88,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Get you mean.","index":15,"end_time":236.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":235.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":16,"end_time":237.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":236.86,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":17,"end_time":237.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":237.5,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Seems like when I think it''s slow, it doesn''t slow down.","index":18,"end_time":240.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":237.98,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"It''s.","index":19,"end_time":241.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":240.9,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Everybody in the brother still wants to pester me.","index":20,"end_time":243.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":241.26,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So.","index":21,"end_time":244.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":243.86,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Question for you.","index":22,"end_time":247.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":245.98,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"That is my screen with you.","index":23,"end_time":250.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":248.14,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Sorry, too many screens.","index":24,"end_time":253.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":250.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, I lost you where you''re at.","index":25,"end_time":255.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":253.7,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Hang on a second here.","index":26,"end_time":256.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":255.02,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Where you at?","index":27,"end_time":256.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":256.14,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Hang on a second.","index":28,"end_time":259.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":258.54,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I apologize.","index":29,"end_time":259.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":259.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No worries.","index":30,"end_time":260.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":260.14,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I know you''re somewhere.","index":31,"end_time":261.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":260.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I can hear you minimize.","index":32,"end_time":266.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":262.29,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s I hate with, you know, multiple screens.","index":33,"end_time":269.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":267.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know, you get it going and.","index":34,"end_time":270.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":269.17,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Then you can''t find people.","index":35,"end_time":271.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":270.29,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"There you are.","index":36,"end_time":271.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":271.21,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":37,"end_time":274.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":273.81,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Hang on a second here.","index":38,"end_time":276.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":275.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Hey there.","index":39,"end_time":279.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":278.93,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"All right, perfect.","index":40,"end_time":282.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":280.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":41,"end_time":283.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":282.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Wanted to ask, I mean, obviously top priority is getting all the website and all that done, but when we roll into January, are we.","index":42,"end_time":290.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":284.21,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I know we''re talking about trying to do some of the videos and some of that stuff too, but are we also going to start, you know, kind of what I''d call an outbound campaign where we''re hitting some of the different, you know, PE firms.","index":43,"end_time":299.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":290.51,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"We''re kind of building target list and some of that.","index":44,"end_time":301.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":299.59,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Some of that stuff will be okay.","index":45,"end_time":302.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":301.35,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Cool.","index":46,"end_time":302.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":302.47,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I mean, obviously I want to get the website done, get collateral.","index":47,"end_time":304.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":302.67,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"All the other stuff you''re doing.","index":48,"end_time":305.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":304.99,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"You guys are running on the right path.","index":49,"end_time":307.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":305.99,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I was just curious because we hadn''t talked about that.","index":50,"end_time":309.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":307.39,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So do we have the presentation for you today?","index":51,"end_time":312.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":309.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, cool.","index":52,"end_time":314.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":313.35,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"All right, let''s do it.","index":53,"end_time":315.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":314.15,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I like it.","index":54,"end_time":315.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":315.35,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":55,"end_time":316.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":316.28,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And I see that Kristen just joined as well.","index":56,"end_time":319.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":317.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Hey, how''s it going, Kristen?","index":57,"end_time":322.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":321.08,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Good.","index":58,"end_time":322.68,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":322.36,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"How are you guys doing?","index":59,"end_time":323.84,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":322.68,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"All right.","index":60,"end_time":324.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":323.84,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Got any holiday plans?","index":61,"end_time":327.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":326.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"She''s working.","index":62,"end_time":329.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":329.08,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I didn''t give her any time off.","index":63,"end_time":331.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":329.88,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"There you go.","index":64,"end_time":332.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":332.12,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Keep busy.","index":65,"end_time":334.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":333.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, she.","index":66,"end_time":335.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":334.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"She''s going to.","index":67,"end_time":336.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":335.92,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"She''s going to be calling, beg me.","index":68,"end_time":337.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":336.56,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"She''s got two small kids, so they''re going to be bonking off the walls and she''s going to call and ask me what I can give her to do so she can come up excuse and I have to do it exactly.","index":69,"end_time":345.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":337.68,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"In the back of me.","index":70,"end_time":347.82,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":347.02,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"How old are your kids, Kristen?","index":71,"end_time":350.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":348.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I have a 3 and a 4 year old.","index":72,"end_time":353.26,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":350.62,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"That''s awesome.","index":73,"end_time":354.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":353.5,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I have a 11 month old or she''ll be 11 months in a few days.","index":74,"end_time":358.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":354.3,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It only gets funner.","index":75,"end_time":360.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":359.02,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Yes, very exciting.","index":76,"end_time":361.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":360.46,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":77,"end_time":363.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":363.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, well, we''ll dive in.","index":78,"end_time":365.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":363.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Definitely a lot of things to go over today.","index":79,"end_time":367.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":365.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Just give me one second to adjust my screenshot.","index":80,"end_time":372.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":369.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Right.","index":81,"end_time":372.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":372.29,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So, Michael, actually the first thing that we had slated for the agenda was the ABM plan.","index":82,"end_time":377.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":374.29,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So you just asked about Outbound.","index":83,"end_time":379.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":377.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"This is the strategy that we have proposed and we''ll, we''ll share the, the long form document with you and then we go through some of the updates on the website process.","index":84,"end_time":389.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":379.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And we''ve also developed a preliminary content calendar that we would like to work with you guys on and just a status update on the logos.","index":85,"end_time":396.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":389.57,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":86,"end_time":397.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":396.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, so we have the ABM plan.","index":87,"end_time":400.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":398.57,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''ll go ahead and open up this document.","index":88,"end_time":402.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":400.73,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It is, I think, a little over 30 pages, so I''m not going to read through that today, but I''ll share that with you guys to review in depth at a high level.","index":89,"end_time":411.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":402.81,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s about focus and leverage of ktc.","index":90,"end_time":414.089,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":411.25,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So you guys have grown historically through referrals, which is great, but it is unpredictable.","index":91,"end_time":419.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":414.65,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know, you can''t have a solid pipeline when you''re just counting on referrals.","index":92,"end_time":423.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":419.77,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So what this document does is outlines how we take the momentum of the company that you''ve built and turn it into something a little bit more intentional, meaning a really narrow focus with the PE operating partners, portfolio, company leaders, and all of the content that we''re producing for that.","index":93,"end_time":440.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":423.85,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And sending through email and LinkedIn messaging and ads is really showing how KTC is a senior speed first alternative, especially considered to like a Korn fairy who''s like, hey, our first 30 days, you''re gonna walk through our process and then.","index":94,"end_time":456.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":440.29,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''Re going to talk to you.","index":95,"end_time":457.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":456.11,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And really builds like a simple marketing engine that keeps KTC visible with the right account.","index":96,"end_time":462.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":458.39,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So is the first email sent to someone going to get them to reach out to you right away?","index":97,"end_time":467.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":463.11,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"More than likely not.","index":98,"end_time":469.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":467.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But when they see a few emails, then they start to see some ads, they visit the website, they get retargeted with more ads.","index":99,"end_time":474.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":469.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We reach out to them on LinkedIn, they see a podcast episode.","index":100,"end_time":477.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":474.83,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All of these data points are part of the journey of them becoming a prospect and eventually a client of ktc.","index":101,"end_time":484.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":477.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So not about a lot of volume right away, but about being top of mind and showing needs.","index":102,"end_time":490.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":485.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then when we do that consistently and in front of the right people, that is when all of a sudden KTC becomes back of the mind when they are like, we have to make a hire, where do we go?","index":103,"end_time":501.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":490.81,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I''LL do a quick preview of the document, but there''s a table of contents in here to simplify it and then it goes through an executive summary as well.","index":104,"end_time":510.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":503.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But this goes into how we''re targeting, who we''re targeting, what we''re going to talk about, how the website becomes a factor of this, how the content engine becomes a fact factor of this.","index":105,"end_time":519.869,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":510.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So everything is layered out in extreme.","index":106,"end_time":522.669,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":519.869,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Detail so that we''re transparent across the board on all plans.","index":107,"end_time":525.789,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":522.669,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":108,"end_time":526.589,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":526.029,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And then he.","index":109,"end_time":527.349,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":526.589,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"The.","index":110,"end_time":527.549,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":527.349,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"One of the things I know Justin talked about and I''m sure in there is I didn''t.","index":111,"end_time":530.949,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":527.549,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"We didn''t put any, you know, obviously do the aba.","index":112,"end_time":533.949,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":530.949,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But our.","index":113,"end_time":534.509,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":533.949,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But are we also going to look at paid ads or two and some of that as we roll through to.","index":114,"end_time":539.349,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":535.469,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Okay, yeah.","index":115,"end_time":539.869,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":539.349,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So paid ads is a component of this.","index":116,"end_time":541.309,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":539.869,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":117,"end_time":541.669,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":541.309,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Okay.","index":118,"end_time":542.069,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":541.669,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yep.","index":119,"end_time":542.589,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":542.069,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And we have a recommended budget in here of three grand.","index":120,"end_time":545.709,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":542.829,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We can obviously talk about that with you.","index":121,"end_time":547.709,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":545.949,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But yeah, that''s what we recommended to get started.","index":122,"end_time":551.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":548.82,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then everything that we do is backed by data.","index":123,"end_time":553.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":551.3,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we''re going to review the performance after we launch these campaigns on a regular, ongoing basis and see what tweaks we need to make.","index":124,"end_time":560.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":553.46,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I don''t like to start by saying we''re just going to send them seven emails in two months.","index":125,"end_time":563.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":560.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''re going to come back and see how it went.","index":126,"end_time":565.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":563.9,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, we''re going to start with probably four emails and then we''re going to look week over week, you know, subject line comparisons, what''s performing better, what''s driving people to the website and ultimately what''s leading to more form fills.","index":127,"end_time":576.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":565.3,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, cool question.","index":128,"end_time":577.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":576.47,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I have one quick question for you on different topics.","index":129,"end_time":579.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":577.67,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So obviously we''re on Zoom.","index":130,"end_time":582.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":579.91,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And you know, part of what you guys are doing is, you know, you guys will get all the contact lists because I know you guys use Clay.","index":131,"end_time":587.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":582.71,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"When I talked to Justin, I know you guys have an agreement with them.","index":132,"end_time":592.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":589.19,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So I''m getting to the point where I may drop Zoom because it sounds like at least from even what my HubSpot folks said from the integration, Clay gives you better interaction and playing back and forth.","index":133,"end_time":602.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":592.15,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I.","index":134,"end_time":604.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":604.48,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"You go to their website and you get some pricing, you try to ask them to have somebody call you.","index":135,"end_time":609.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":605.04,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Nobody does.","index":136,"end_time":610.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":609.76,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"If I want to buy a subscription from Clay, is that something you guys can help me broker or get me hooked up to somebody?","index":137,"end_time":616.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":610.72,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Just from a standpoint is I know.","index":138,"end_time":617.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":616.72,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"You guys are gonna provide.","index":139,"end_time":618.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":617.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You guys are gonna get the leads and get the information is.","index":140,"end_time":623.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":621.04,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But some of the other stuff that we have, I like it just to be able to.","index":141,"end_time":625.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":623.24,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Where I can populate some of the stuff with the, with our CRM into HubSpot.","index":142,"end_time":629.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":625.84,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So if we''re trying to get clean data and stuff like that.","index":143,"end_time":631.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":629.68,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Now our ats, you know, everybody seems to be investing in their AI and pulling data, so their stuff is actually pretty good about pulling some of the data.","index":144,"end_time":639.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":631.92,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But what I liked about Zoom was it did have some of that AI, but it also kind of showed org charts.","index":145,"end_time":645.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":639.22,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Some of their data I think is a little stale.","index":146,"end_time":647.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":645.74,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"They don''t always are staying on top of it.","index":147,"end_time":649.299,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":647.5,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Where I think Justin had said that you guys have seen Clay has actually done a better job of saying some of the updates.","index":148,"end_time":654.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":649.299,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But I can''t seem to get anybody to call me back.","index":149,"end_time":657.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":655.18,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"You know, I''ve sat on a couple podcasts and say, hey, I''m interested in buying.","index":150,"end_time":660.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":657.3,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Can somebody call me back?","index":151,"end_time":661.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":660.38,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Nobody calls me.","index":152,"end_time":662.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":661.84,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So I didn''t know if that''s something you guys can help me broker a deal on or if I. Yeah, procure or something like that.","index":153,"end_time":668.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":662.76,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So yeah, it''s actually really interesting because they used to have a self serve model and so when you brought that up, I just checked out their website and it does look like you have to contact them.","index":154,"end_time":675.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":668.08,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we''ll reach out to our rep and try and get that conversation going because yeah, I mean we used to just sign up and.","index":155,"end_time":682.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":675.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Or when we created the account, you know, we just signed up and then upgraded our account.","index":156,"end_time":685.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":682.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So yeah, perfect.","index":157,"end_time":686.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":685.68,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yep.","index":158,"end_time":687.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":686.8,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So sorry to digress.","index":159,"end_time":688.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":687.35,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"That was my only question.","index":160,"end_time":689.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":688.31,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Just I had asked you guys because like I said, I''ve been trying for three weeks to get somebody to call me and I.","index":161,"end_time":693.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":689.19,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Nobody calls.","index":162,"end_time":695.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":694.31,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s frustrating.","index":163,"end_time":697.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":695.83,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":164,"end_time":697.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":697.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, cool.","index":165,"end_time":699.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":698.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yep, we''ll definitely reach out to them.","index":166,"end_time":701.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":699.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But yeah, if you have any questions as we send over the document to review, just let us know.","index":167,"end_time":708.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":703.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":168,"end_time":708.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":708.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Then we also have some more pages built out, designed in for the website.","index":169,"end_time":715.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":710.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And so let me open up here.","index":170,"end_time":720.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":715.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"This is just kind of like a macro view of the pages that we have designed and written so far.","index":171,"end_time":726.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":721.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So making great progress.","index":172,"end_time":727.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":726.39,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And what we''ve done is added these into a tool we call Markup.","index":173,"end_time":731.389,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":727.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And so we''ll share a link with you and this will just give you a chance.","index":174,"end_time":734.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":731.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"This is literally a drag.","index":175,"end_time":736.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":735.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Just click around and leave any comment.","index":176,"end_time":738.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":736.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So you just click here and say, you know, I want this to be an 87% success rate.","index":177,"end_time":743.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":738.83,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Anything like that.","index":178,"end_time":744.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":744.11,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And all of the pages are just right here.","index":179,"end_time":746.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":744.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You can scroll up top.","index":180,"end_time":748.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":747.21,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yep, perfect.","index":181,"end_time":749.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":748.25,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Looks good.","index":182,"end_time":749.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":749.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":183,"end_time":751.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":750.73,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So, yeah, recently it was the executive page, the Resources page, contingency hiring and our services.","index":184,"end_time":758.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":753.21,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":185,"end_time":759.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":758.65,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Now the re.","index":186,"end_time":761.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":760.89,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Quick question.","index":187,"end_time":762.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":761.81,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"When you go back to resource spaces, we talk about contig hiring the executive and you guys, I''m sure obviously are doing, you know, SEO, but in MySpace, more people when they''re doing search, they''re going to retain search for this or that.","index":188,"end_time":774.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":762.25,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So just want to make sure as you guys and my services make sure that contingent and retained.","index":189,"end_time":779.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":774.37,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"We highlight that just because I know people sometimes will search for hey, who''s the top retained search that does this?","index":190,"end_time":784.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":779.27,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So hopefully we pop up in a search.","index":191,"end_time":786.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":785.11,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So.","index":192,"end_time":787.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":786.71,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yep, yeah, absolutely.","index":193,"end_time":788.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":787.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":194,"end_time":789.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":789.11,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And.","index":195,"end_time":789.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":789.47,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And we''ve been doing SEO work that that was the kind of one of the main purposes of rewriting the content.","index":196,"end_time":794.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":789.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So.","index":197,"end_time":795.069,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":794.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, not looking to lose any momentum of keyword rankings that you''ve built, but enhanced by adding some more.","index":198,"end_time":799.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":795.069,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, totally fine.","index":199,"end_time":800.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":799.91,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yep.","index":200,"end_time":801.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":800.75,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Hey, what we did I think was pretty bad.","index":201,"end_time":803.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":801.43,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So anything you guys can do, hopefully it''ll prove it.","index":202,"end_time":805.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":803.31,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So.","index":203,"end_time":806.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":805.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, we can even send you like we have a whole table that outlines like the keywords that we''re choosing for.","index":204,"end_time":810.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":806.45,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Different pages as well.","index":205,"end_time":811.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":810.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":206,"end_time":812.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":811.65,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Kristen, when we met and last week, Michael, when we met as well, we talked about developing the content calendar.","index":207,"end_time":818.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":813.65,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And so we have this preliminary document built and I kind of just want to walk through what it is.","index":208,"end_time":823.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":818.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So this will be an ongoing living document that we work on in tandem.","index":209,"end_time":828.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":823.81,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So anytime.","index":210,"end_time":829.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":828.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know, Michael, you mentioned last week, you''re like, hey, I''m going to have a conversation with this guy that I placed.","index":211,"end_time":833.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":829.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Want to see if he''s interested.","index":212,"end_time":835.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":833.88,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know, we''ll give you access.","index":213,"end_time":836.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":835.24,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So you can just go in, you can add his name in here.","index":214,"end_time":839.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":836.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You don''t have to come up with a title or anything like that.","index":215,"end_time":841.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":839.08,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You can just say like, I already.","index":216,"end_time":842.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":841.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Talked to him and whenever you.","index":217,"end_time":844.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":842.92,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"We want to do him, his.","index":218,"end_time":845.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":844.28,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"His name is Darren.","index":219,"end_time":846.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":845.64,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"He''s already said he''s more than happy to do anytime we want.","index":220,"end_time":849.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":846.6,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So I already cleared him and he''s ready to go.","index":221,"end_time":851.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":849.68,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So.","index":222,"end_time":852.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":851.88,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":223,"end_time":853.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":852.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s awesome.","index":224,"end_time":854.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":853.4,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"It''s D D E R I N. Last name is P I T R E and his title is EVP Sales Utilities over at Sunbath Sunbelt Solemn.","index":225,"end_time":867.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":854.12,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"That''s.","index":226,"end_time":871.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":870.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, go back one more O.","index":227,"end_time":874.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":871.83,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So there you go.","index":228,"end_time":875.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":874.31,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"S O L O M O N Solomon.","index":229,"end_time":880.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":876.79,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Gotcha.","index":230,"end_time":880.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":880.39,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Okay, perfect.","index":231,"end_time":881.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":880.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, we just added some fields in here also.","index":232,"end_time":886.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":884.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So you know, if we wanted to rotate who the host is, we can just indicate that in the drop down.","index":233,"end_time":889.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":886.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But what we''ll do is so you can see here we''ve Just come up with like 10 off the cuff topics.","index":234,"end_time":895.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":891,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We can work with you guys on these to refine them.","index":235,"end_time":897.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":895.48,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And what we tend to do for our clients, and it''s up to you if you want to use them or not, is develop a framework.","index":236,"end_time":902.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":898.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I touched on this a little bit last week.","index":237,"end_time":904.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":903.16,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s not a script for you guys to follow, but just here''s trends that we''re seeing.","index":238,"end_time":908.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":904.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We even give the guests some like.","index":239,"end_time":909.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":908.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Talking points if they''re interested as well.","index":240,"end_time":911.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":909.88,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, I think we should do that.","index":241,"end_time":912.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":911.72,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"The more, the more, the easier to make it for people, the better.","index":242,"end_time":915.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":912.92,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":243,"end_time":916.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":915.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And we''ll design a letterhead for you guys as well so that you can.","index":244,"end_time":918.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":916.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Send it like with KTC Search Branding.","index":245,"end_time":920.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":918.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":246,"end_time":921.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":921.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":247,"end_time":922.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":922.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we''ll share access to this document with you guys and you can feel free to edit anything.","index":248,"end_time":926.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":922.9,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And as we start publishing episodes, you''ll see, you know, we''ll have the frameworks here, but whether it''s published or not, where it''s been published, the dates, the.","index":249,"end_time":934.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":926.54,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"URLs, everything like that.","index":250,"end_time":936.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":934.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Now the other thing that we can do too is if you guys want, since we''re not part of Richie May, but like I said, I can get Jason.","index":251,"end_time":942.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":936.98,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"He''ll, he''ll, we can interview him.","index":252,"end_time":944.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":942.34,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But the other one, I was thinking because she''s got a high energy and she''s very knowledgeable, is we may want to, and you guys think about how we want to use her.","index":253,"end_time":951.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":944.38,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But Felicia, who''s the CMO for Richie Mae, you know, she''ll, you know, I''ve done a bunch, I''m helping her build out her new team right now.","index":254,"end_time":960.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":951.31,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So I mean, she''s good, she''s got high energy, high drive, she''s good on camera.","index":255,"end_time":963.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":960.39,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So figure out how we want to use her.","index":256,"end_time":966.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":964.03,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Because she could obviously talk about, you know, what I''ve done for her, but what also makes me, you know, what makes me different.","index":257,"end_time":973.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":967.47,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I mean, she''ll talk about me as different than you guys ought to put that in past tense, you know, to phrase it as ktc.","index":258,"end_time":979.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":973.23,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But you know, obviously her, her experience is going to be dealing with me.","index":259,"end_time":982.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":979.19,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So.","index":260,"end_time":982.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":982.53,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, I think that''s a super strong person to have.","index":261,"end_time":986.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":982.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know, whether it''s testimonials that we get out of there or just the content series itself, social media assets, everything.","index":262,"end_time":992.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":986.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"My one question there is, with your timeline of like not being able to be a spokesperson on this, would it just be her?","index":263,"end_time":1000.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":992.65,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Would it be Kristen talking to her or would we wait until.","index":264,"end_time":1002.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1000.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We could probably have maybe have one of you guys Interview her.","index":265,"end_time":1006.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1002.57,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Or we could, you know, whatever.","index":266,"end_time":1007.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1006.13,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Because, I mean, you guys, marketer to marketer.","index":267,"end_time":1009.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1007.29,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I mean, whatever you think you want.","index":268,"end_time":1010.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1009.21,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"You guys kind of give a script of what we want to accompl, and then one of you guys can kind of interview.","index":269,"end_time":1014.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1010.45,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And then we can always gloss it over, however, at a later date or something like that.","index":270,"end_time":1017.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1014.07,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So.","index":271,"end_time":1018.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1017.75,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah, because she''d be a good spokesperson.","index":272,"end_time":1019.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1018.11,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And then, you know, from that standpoint.","index":273,"end_time":1021.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1019.95,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And then I''m also working on my.","index":274,"end_time":1023.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1021.59,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Probably to get that done is I''ll probably also get that one.","index":275,"end_time":1028.509,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1023.67,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"We might have to position.","index":276,"end_time":1030.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1028.509,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But I''ll probably also get Alex, who''s The principal for F3.","index":277,"end_time":1034.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1030.87,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"The.","index":278,"end_time":1034.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1034.39,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"The PE firm owns us.","index":279,"end_time":1035.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1034.63,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"He''ll.","index":280,"end_time":1036.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1035.95,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"He''ll.","index":281,"end_time":1036.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1036.31,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I can probably also get him on camera too, but I won''t be able to get him until probably January.","index":282,"end_time":1039.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1036.71,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Okay.","index":283,"end_time":1040.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1040.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, those are awesome.","index":284,"end_time":1041.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1040.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If you don''t mind sending me, like, their LinkedIn profile.","index":285,"end_time":1045.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1041.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, we''ll build a framework and do some research on a topic, and then we just find that people are much more interested if we, like, if we''re not just kind of out of the blue and we''re like, here''s what we want to talk about all.","index":286,"end_time":1055.239,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1045.24,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":287,"end_time":1055.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1055.239,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yep, yep.","index":288,"end_time":1056.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1055.84,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And then, like I said is I can also use Randy.","index":289,"end_time":1059.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1056.56,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Randy''s.","index":290,"end_time":1060.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1059.44,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"The CRO that we placed over at emc.","index":291,"end_time":1062.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1060.12,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I can get probably Oak Tree.","index":292,"end_time":1065.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1063.76,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I got to work them a little bit.","index":293,"end_time":1066.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1065.6,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"They got a bunch of stuff going.","index":294,"end_time":1067.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1066.6,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So I''m going to talk to Nick, who''s my main guy over there.","index":295,"end_time":1070,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1067.52,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But.","index":296,"end_time":1070.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1070,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But I''m pretty confident that, you know, he''ll.","index":297,"end_time":1073.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1070.35,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"He''ll be willing to have a conversation.","index":298,"end_time":1074.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1073.11,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"He probably wouldn''t want to do an interview.","index":299,"end_time":1075.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1074.67,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"It''d be part more about.","index":300,"end_time":1076.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1075.83,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Hey, you guys, have a call with him, collect a bunch of data points.","index":301,"end_time":1079.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1076.79,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"He can talk about industry and then you can take the data and then we can kind of maybe, maybe you interview me or something else and you put the two together.","index":302,"end_time":1085.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1079.23,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Whatever.","index":303,"end_time":1086.229,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1085.71,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But he''ll.","index":304,"end_time":1087.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1086.229,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I''m.","index":305,"end_time":1087.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1087.11,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I''m sure he''ll be willing to do it, but he won''t want to sit through a podcast and more.","index":306,"end_time":1090.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1087.51,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Well, hey, let''s go through something.","index":307,"end_time":1091.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1090.75,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I''m happy to say how good you are.","index":308,"end_time":1093.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1091.99,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Whatever.","index":309,"end_time":1093.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1093.31,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And then you guys kind of take and do whatever you want with it.","index":310,"end_time":1096.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1093.79,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yep.","index":311,"end_time":1096.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1096.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, we can absolutely work with that.","index":312,"end_time":1098.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1096.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":313,"end_time":1100.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1099.81,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Kristen, any questions on anything so far?","index":314,"end_time":1103.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1101.73,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, I just put a note, Michael, for you and I to circle back on this during our one on one to talk about dates so that we''re kind of.","index":315,"end_time":1114.33,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1104.77,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"I want to make sure we''re Working towards stuff versus we have a list.","index":316,"end_time":1118.21,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1114.33,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"But then all of a sudden, Q1 ends and we say, wait a minute, we didn''t do anything here.","index":317,"end_time":1122.77,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1118.21,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Yep.","index":318,"end_time":1123.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1123.12,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":319,"end_time":1123.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1123.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And we can even add more columns if we want to have, like a column for recording date, etc.","index":320,"end_time":1127.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1123.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":321,"end_time":1127.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1127.2,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":322,"end_time":1128.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1127.76,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I think before, you know, some of these things, like, we can schedule whatever, but I think, you know, kind of what we talked about is I want to make sure the site''s done all that''s live.","index":323,"end_time":1136,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1128.12,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"You know, we got some of the collateral stuff because obviously once we start, you know, sending stuff out or you guys think, I want to make sure that we''re sending them to the new site and everything else is looking good.","index":324,"end_time":1146.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1136.08,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So that way they have a brand as it.","index":325,"end_time":1149.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1146.28,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"You know, how we want to.","index":326,"end_time":1150.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1149.72,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"How we.","index":327,"end_time":1151,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1150.64,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"How we would position that.","index":328,"end_time":1152.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1151,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So 100%.","index":329,"end_time":1153.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1152.16,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then, Kristen, I know you emailed about the logo, so we got the colors.","index":330,"end_time":1161.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1157.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Thank you for sending those over the other night, Michael.","index":331,"end_time":1163.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1161.59,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we''re.","index":332,"end_time":1165.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1164.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''re working on those.","index":333,"end_time":1166.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1165.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Our team is a little bit in and out this week just with the holiday.","index":334,"end_time":1169.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1166.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we''ll have the updated new green versions that were more green than this.","index":335,"end_time":1173.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1170.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Kristen, based on your feedback on Monday.","index":336,"end_time":1176.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1173.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, I like, I like those.","index":337,"end_time":1178.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1177.19,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Those all look good.","index":338,"end_time":1179.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1178.39,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Oh, you like these?","index":339,"end_time":1180.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1179.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, those look pretty good.","index":340,"end_time":1181.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1180.28,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I mean, I liked how you''re doing the color.","index":341,"end_time":1182.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1181.28,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Now my only question is B.","index":342,"end_time":1184,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1182.76,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Is.","index":343,"end_time":1184.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1184,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Is there.","index":344,"end_time":1184.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1184.2,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And once again, you guys are the marketing people.","index":345,"end_time":1186.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1184.6,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I''m just spitballing in this could.","index":346,"end_time":1187.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1186.36,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"You could say it''s stupid idea, Mike, but you know how you guys have KTC in the black?","index":347,"end_time":1191.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1187.8,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"We can we mess with any of those where we get some of the different colors of maybe some of their colors into it.","index":348,"end_time":1196.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1192.04,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Once again, I don''t want to make it look like a freaking clown, but whatever.","index":349,"end_time":1200.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1196.88,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But I like how you blend it just even.","index":350,"end_time":1201.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1200.12,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Just getting a little glean and some of the stuff into the kitchen.","index":351,"end_time":1205.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1201.88,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I think that, that looks.","index":352,"end_time":1206.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1205.43,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"That looks pretty good.","index":353,"end_time":1207.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1206.55,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So.","index":354,"end_time":1207.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1207.55,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But I mean.","index":355,"end_time":1208.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1207.83,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Okay, yeah, you guys are.","index":356,"end_time":1209.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1208.23,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"You guys are going the right direction.","index":357,"end_time":1210.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1209.47,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I''ll put it that way.","index":358,"end_time":1211.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1210.79,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":359,"end_time":1211.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1211.63,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Okay, great.","index":360,"end_time":1212.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1211.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Well, we''ll still.","index":361,"end_time":1212.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1212.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''ll.","index":362,"end_time":1213.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1212.91,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"We''ll keep on then for the.","index":363,"end_time":1214.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1213.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The other version that Kristen asked for.","index":364,"end_time":1216.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1214.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And yet we can create some versions of this where maybe we have like the gradient rolling through the text or just some different logo marks that we can play with.","index":365,"end_time":1225.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1216.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, okay.","index":366,"end_time":1225.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1225.11,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":367,"end_time":1226.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1225.83,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Because what, you know, the thing is, is if you, when you go to their site, a lot of.","index":368,"end_time":1229.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1226.23,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Well, this I, you know, and this could be Q1, it could be Q2.","index":369,"end_time":1232.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1229.39,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"It may not be to 27, but knowing eventually I may have to integrate in there.","index":370,"end_time":1237.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1232.11,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"The more, the more stuff that it looks like it''s a little bit like there''s.","index":371,"end_time":1241.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1237.6,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I''m not going to have to change anything.","index":372,"end_time":1242.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1241.64,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And my conversations with Felicia is, hey, whenever it integrates in, we''re kind of self contained.","index":373,"end_time":1248.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1242.96,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I already, you know, I told her I had you guys saying she''s.","index":374,"end_time":1250.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1248.4,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"That''s perfect, you know, because each department is somewhat outsourced their, their thing.","index":375,"end_time":1254.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1250.48,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And since I''m coming, I said, look, I already have my own marketing group.","index":376,"end_time":1257.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1254.84,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So she''s on board with that.","index":377,"end_time":1259.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1257.48,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"All she asked is, hey, when we do it.","index":378,"end_time":1261.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1259.24,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And to be determined, it could be end of first quarter.","index":379,"end_time":1264.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1261.48,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"It could be in fourth quarter.","index":380,"end_time":1265.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1264.36,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"You know, we have a lot of other priorities of what that is and that''ll be decided by Alex pe when he wants to bring it in.","index":381,"end_time":1271.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1265.76,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But at least so that way we''re not.","index":382,"end_time":1273.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1271.96,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"If they drop us on the site, we don''t look like we''re a total right.","index":383,"end_time":1277.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1273.88,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Oddball compared to everything else that''s sitting on the site.","index":384,"end_time":1279.719,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1277.24,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yep.","index":385,"end_time":1280.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1279.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, totally hear you.","index":386,"end_time":1281.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1280.68,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And Kristen gave us the same feedback.","index":387,"end_time":1282.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1281.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":388,"end_time":1283.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1283,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"That''s where I said, Michael, that''s where I said could we go a little bit more green on.","index":389,"end_time":1287.76,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1283.56,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Yeah, exactly.","index":390,"end_time":1288.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1287.76,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yep.","index":391,"end_time":1288.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1288.44,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yep.","index":392,"end_time":1289.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1288.72,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"You guys are heading the right side.","index":393,"end_time":1290.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1289.32,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yep.","index":394,"end_time":1290.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1290.36,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Those are definitely heading the right direction.","index":395,"end_time":1292.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1290.72,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yep.","index":396,"end_time":1292.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1292.6,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Head in the right direction.","index":397,"end_time":1293.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1292.88,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Definitely.","index":398,"end_time":1294.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1293.92,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":399,"end_time":1295.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1294.68,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then we''ll.","index":400,"end_time":1296.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1295.48,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Once we do that, then you''ll be able to give us marks and everything for email signatures and then letterhead and all that other good stuff too, right?","index":401,"end_time":1303.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1296.68,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, we can make that stuff.","index":402,"end_time":1305.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1303.84,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":403,"end_time":1306.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1305.24,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then one other thing and just as if you guys are doing the mark is, is once we kind of line on it, if we end up coming, say, hey, you know, you''re below that a Richie May company or something like that.","index":404,"end_time":1316.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1306.28,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"You know, you''ve probably seen stuff like that.","index":405,"end_time":1317.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1316.08,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yep.","index":406,"end_time":1318,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1317.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Maybe just kind of think of a version like that too.","index":407,"end_time":1319.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1318,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So that way if we, we know it''s going to start branding.","index":408,"end_time":1323.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1320.04,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I may start branding.","index":409,"end_time":1323.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1323.09,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Hey, I''m a, you know, I can''t do it until paperwork signed and stuff like that.","index":410,"end_time":1327.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1323.97,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But I, I rather be ahead of the game.","index":411,"end_time":1330.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1327.73,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So that way if we''re rolling through this other stuff, we don''t have to stop what you guys are doing to hurry up and come up with something, you know, that we can throw up on the website.","index":412,"end_time":1337.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1330.45,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, that''s no problem at all.","index":413,"end_time":1339.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1337.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":414,"end_time":1340.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1339.77,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And we would just need to know like, do they want it to say original company?","index":415,"end_time":1342.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1340.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Rm I Don''t know.","index":416,"end_time":1346.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1343.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Talent Solutions.","index":417,"end_time":1347.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1346.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know, there''s a few different things that I''ve seen.","index":418,"end_time":1349.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1347.29,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So yeah, just let us know.","index":419,"end_time":1350.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1349.45,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Or if it''s just like they have the.","index":420,"end_time":1353.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1350.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The Utah logo here, you know.","index":421,"end_time":1355.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1353.48,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yes, exactly.","index":422,"end_time":1356.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1355.24,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah, something like that.","index":423,"end_time":1357.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1356.16,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Where.","index":424,"end_time":1357.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1357.12,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Because basically what the way we were going to brand was we would go under RM''s.","index":425,"end_time":1361.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1357.44,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"RM Talent Solutions.","index":426,"end_time":1363.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1362.68,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So I think I sent you the mark that Felicia had kind of developed on that.","index":427,"end_time":1366.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1363.96,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So however you guys want to wordsmith it.","index":428,"end_time":1369.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1367.239,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I mean now, like I said, I mean this could be halfway through the year.","index":429,"end_time":1372.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1369.48,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But like I said, I''d rather.","index":430,"end_time":1373.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1372.56,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"If we''re doing all this early, let''s get this out of the way.","index":431,"end_time":1376.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1373.52,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So that way it''s sitting in an archive and if we need it, we can pull it in.","index":432,"end_time":1379.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1376.28,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"If we don''t, then so be able to.","index":433,"end_time":1380.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1379.08,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Okay, yeah, I got you.","index":434,"end_time":1381.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1380.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":435,"end_time":1383.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1382.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then the last thing I wanted.","index":436,"end_time":1385,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1383.48,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"To just go over and it''s updating.","index":437,"end_time":1388.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1385,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"A little bit right now, but just going back through Pulse, the portal.","index":438,"end_time":1392.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1388.12,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So the web page copy and design.","index":439,"end_time":1394.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1392.24,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So the link to review is right here.","index":440,"end_time":1396.599,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1394.68,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So that''ll open up right into the markup where you can leave feedback.","index":441,"end_time":1400.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1397.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":442,"end_time":1401.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1401.08,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And then you can see everything else that we''re working on.","index":443,"end_time":1404.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1402.2,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So for deliverables we will be closing out obviously this was due today, so we''ll be closing out the ABM plan document.","index":444,"end_time":1412.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1404.76,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''ll give you a link to review that.","index":445,"end_time":1413.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1412.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then here are the updated logos and everything else that we''re working on.","index":446,"end_time":1417.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1413.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Thanks, bud.","index":447,"end_time":1418.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1418,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Cool, that''s good.","index":448,"end_time":1419.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1418.6,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Thanks guys.","index":449,"end_time":1420.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1419.76,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah, thank you.","index":450,"end_time":1421.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1420.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Any questions or anything that we did not cover that you were hoping to talk through?","index":451,"end_time":1425.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1421.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Nope.","index":452,"end_time":1425.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1425.2,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"That''s good.","index":453,"end_time":1426.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1425.68,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"You answered my question about the clay.","index":454,"end_time":1427.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1426.04,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"If you guys can help me with that.","index":455,"end_time":1428.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1427.32,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And then the.","index":456,"end_time":1430.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1428.44,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Oh, is.","index":457,"end_time":1432.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1431.52,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Is there anything?","index":458,"end_time":1432.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1432.16,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Well, that''s right.","index":459,"end_time":1434.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1433.2,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"You guys are HubSpot developers too.","index":460,"end_time":1437,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1434.12,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So we.","index":461,"end_time":1437.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1437,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"At once the Columbia folks are done.","index":462,"end_time":1439.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1437.4,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"If we need to change anything, you guys can just bake that into playing to change what we want.","index":463,"end_time":1442.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1439.48,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":464,"end_time":1442.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1442.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"100.","index":465,"end_time":1443.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1442.84,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":466,"end_time":1444.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1443.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, because I think they were going to set up like a separate dashboard for the stuff that you guys were pushing in.","index":467,"end_time":1448.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1444.2,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So that way we could track that but you guys can see what we.","index":468,"end_time":1452.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1448.24,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Can build it all.","index":469,"end_time":1452.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1452.32,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":470,"end_time":1453.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1452.92,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"If we need to change it, you.","index":471,"end_time":1454.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1453.2,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Guys go ahead and change it.","index":472,"end_time":1455.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1454.16,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So.","index":473,"end_time":1455.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1455.08,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yep.","index":474,"end_time":1455.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1455.32,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yep.","index":475,"end_time":1456.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1455.68,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":476,"end_time":1457.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1456.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Hey Colin, earlier you mentioned data and tracking some of the front of the funnel marketing.","index":477,"end_time":1464.32,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1457.84,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Just curious, is that data exportable or is that something that you all are only able to show on your end?","index":478,"end_time":1474.7,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1464.86,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"So what we do is we actually build it''s called a data box.","index":479,"end_time":1478.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1474.94,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s just a platform that we use.","index":480,"end_time":1480.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1478.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Let me see if I can just find an example to show.","index":481,"end_time":1482.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1480.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Basically, it''s one platform.","index":482,"end_time":1484.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1482.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You have one link, and it shows any metric, really, that we want to show for the campaigns, and we can tie that into HubSpot and the email performance and ads and everything, et cetera.","index":483,"end_time":1493.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1484.54,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":484,"end_time":1494.73,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1494.33,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Okay, that''s helpful.","index":485,"end_time":1496.17,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1494.81,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"So huge.","index":486,"end_time":1499.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1498.57,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":487,"end_time":1499.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1499.13,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Because once you guys build everything out, what the goal would be is as we''re developing stuff or we''re, you know, the leads, any type of that stuff would.","index":488,"end_time":1506.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1499.37,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Would live in HubSpot.","index":489,"end_time":1508.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1506.49,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So we can try.","index":490,"end_time":1509.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1508.97,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":491,"end_time":1509.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1509.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And we''ll develop those dashboards as well.","index":492,"end_time":1511.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1509.81,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"This is just one that.","index":493,"end_time":1512.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1511.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"For activities outside of HubSpot.","index":494,"end_time":1514.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1512.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So, like, you know, this is connected.","index":495,"end_time":1515.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1514.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"To their company page, for example, or their website, and we''ll keep building out.","index":496,"end_time":1520.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1515.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"For more campaigns that we''re running.","index":497,"end_time":1522.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1520.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":498,"end_time":1523.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1522.6,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"No, that''s perfect.","index":499,"end_time":1523.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1523.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And sorry, lost, because I''m new here.","index":500,"end_time":1527.08,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1525.24,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Does that feed into.","index":501,"end_time":1528.44,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1527.16,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"So once you go live and Michael wanted to go in or I wanted to go in, would we view that in Pulse or would we view that in Data?","index":502,"end_time":1536.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1528.6,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Yeah, so that.","index":503,"end_time":1537.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1536.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So here, I''ll show.","index":504,"end_time":1539.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1537.88,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"One second.","index":505,"end_time":1540.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1539.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So as we build out, just pull that back up.","index":506,"end_time":1543.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1540.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So once we build your data box, it will live under this resources list right here.","index":507,"end_time":1552.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1548.37,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''ll have a link right to it.","index":508,"end_time":1553.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1552.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That link never changes, which is the really cool part.","index":509,"end_time":1556.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1553.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"There''s a bunch of other tools that are like.","index":510,"end_time":1558.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1556.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"They change every time you write something.","index":511,"end_time":1559.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1558.29,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":512,"end_time":1560.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1559.65,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":513,"end_time":1561.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1561.09,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So that''ll live in here.","index":514,"end_time":1562.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1561.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then we also have a report that we work on internally but can share anytime.","index":515,"end_time":1566.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1562.45,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And it shows, like, the most engaged accounts.","index":516,"end_time":1569.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1566.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We use that to basically tell you guys, like, hey, this person didn''t respond.","index":517,"end_time":1573.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1569.73,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But them and a few other peers have been on the website like 10 times in the last two weeks.","index":518,"end_time":1577.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1573.25,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":519,"end_time":1577.85,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1577.57,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"So maybe reach out.","index":520,"end_time":1579.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1577.85,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":521,"end_time":1579.81,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1579.33,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":522,"end_time":1580.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1580.13,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":523,"end_time":1581.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1580.61,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Yeah, Great question.","index":524,"end_time":1583.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1581.25,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Anything else?","index":525,"end_time":1584.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1583.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That is it.","index":526,"end_time":1585.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1584.93,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"That''s it.","index":527,"end_time":1586.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1585.57,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And then when do we do we get together?","index":528,"end_time":1587.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1586.09,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Are you guys off next week?","index":529,"end_time":1589.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1588.21,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Sounds like you are.","index":530,"end_time":1589.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1589.33,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"We are.","index":531,"end_time":1590.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1590.21,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, that''s fine.","index":532,"end_time":1591.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1590.85,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So we get together after that first week back or.","index":533,"end_time":1593.729,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1591.57,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah, that would be great.","index":534,"end_time":1595.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1593.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So, yeah, I just canceled it for next week and we''re slated for the sixth.","index":535,"end_time":1600.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1596.77,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we''ll have a bunch of content to review, website updates to review a whole bunch of stuff.","index":536,"end_time":1605.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1600.37,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, that''s fine.","index":537,"end_time":1606.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1606.1,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And then the other thing just.","index":538,"end_time":1608.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1606.62,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And I don''t know what if we have it that far scheduled out, but the week of the 12th, I have to go out to a target in North Carolina.","index":539,"end_time":1615.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1608.02,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So I''m going to be traveling the 14th, 15th and I don''t get back into the 16th.","index":540,"end_time":1619.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1615.14,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So if we have a meeting that week, we''d either have to do in the beginning of the week or we''re.","index":541,"end_time":1623.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1619.54,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Scheduled on the 13th right now.","index":542,"end_time":1624.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1623.3,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So does that still work?","index":543,"end_time":1625.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1624.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s.","index":544,"end_time":1625.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1625.46,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"That''s fine.","index":545,"end_time":1626.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1625.78,"spe