WITH new_meeting AS (
  INSERT INTO compass_meetings (contract_id, meeting_date, source, external_id, title, participants, duration_seconds, recording_url, transcript, sentiment, raw_metadata, created_at, updated_at)
  VALUES (
    '9e72e3f5-f31f-4c70-870d-79db54b271b2',
    '2025-12-23 16:00:00+00',
    'fireflies',
    '01KCS81BFRNGTNE3C6N3RMXXVG',
    'Weekly Marketing Meeting (Shockoe <> New North)',
    '{"Edwin Huertas","Edwin Huertas","Colin Costigan"}'::text[],
    653,
    'https://us02web.zoom.us/j/88965765122?pwd=mPL1aFvxXYMYFRYawSa6f5Ez7s5Uv6.1',
    '{"id":"01KCS81BFRNGTNE3C6N3RMXXVG","title":"Weekly Marketing Meeting (Shockoe <> New North)","summary":{"notes":"## **Access and Data Handover**\n\nThe team agreed to provide Edwin with all necessary assets and clarify access rights to ensure smooth transition and ongoing work.\n\n- **Colin committed to packaging a Google Drive folder containing all engagement data and lists** for Edwin to use going forward (05:59)  \n    - This archive will include all relevant contact lists and campaign materials  \n    - Colin will also send a comprehensive list of technologies used including those being phased out  \n    - The rationale is to give Edwin full visibility and resources to continue independently  \n    - Packaging and sharing will be completed within the week to avoid delays in Edwin’s work  \n\n- **Edwin confirmed his understanding of which tools will no longer be accessible, mainly those being sunset except for Smart Lead** which remains under consideration (07:11)  \n    - Edwin is preparing to continue list building and outreach with remaining tools and will reach out with questions as needed  \n    - He clarified he has alternative email options beyond Smart Lead, reducing urgency on that front  \n    - He requested clarity on access to forms and website elements to ensure no gaps remain  \n\n## **Tool Usage and Integration**\n\nThe discussion clarified current tool integrations and paused unnecessary tools to align resources with active needs.\n\n- **The team agreed to pause HeyRich campaigns immediately since it is no longer actively used** (08:57)  \n    - Edwin described the process of list building in Clay and subsequent campaign execution in HeyRich  \n    - Colin explained Clay and HeyRich have direct integration for smoother campaign mapping, improving efficiency  \n    - This pause aims to reduce wasted effort and costs from running unused campaigns  \n\n- **Colin suggested Clay’s free tier for list building as a cost-effective option for Edwin to explore independently** (08:36)  \n    - This shows a support mindset to help Edwin maintain momentum after engagement ends  \n    - Tools sunset decisions reflect a strategic focus on simplifying the tech stack  \n\n## **Communication and Support Continuity**\n\nBoth sides expressed positive sentiments and a willingness to support ongoing needs despite winding down.\n\n- **Colin expressed appreciation for the working relationship and wished Edwin well in future efforts** (09:45)  \n    - He acknowledged results were limited but emphasized positive collaboration and future opportunities  \n    - This tone supports a professional handoff and potential future engagement  \n\n- **Edwin reflected on the project’s evolution, noting earlier involvement might have changed outcomes** (10:05)  \n    - He remains optimistic about content and strategy potential with better timing  \n    - He confirmed he knows who to contact for help moving forward  \n\n- **Both exchanged personal well-wishes, reinforcing goodwill and rapport beyond business** (10:33)  \n\n## **Next Steps and Timeline**\n\nKey deliverables and timelines were set to ensure a clean handoff and enable Edwin’s autonomous progress.\n\n- **Colin will deliver the zipped project folder and tools list within the current week** to support Edwin’s next phase (09:34)  \n    - This timeline balances thoroughness with urgency to avoid disruption  \n    - Edwin will continue to send ad hoc requests via Slack during the transition period  \n    - The handoff package includes all critical lists and access details to minimize confusion  \n\n- **Edwin will verify access to website forms and related systems to confirm no outstanding issues** (07:00)  \n    - He already tested form submissions and identified some address changes, showing proactive problem-solving  \n    - Nina’s recent updates resolved some email routing issues, improving lead follow-up quality  \n\nThis plan positions Edwin to proceed independently with clear resources, while the team wraps up remaining support efficiently.","outline":null,"keywords":["Smart Lead","list building","tool access","Clay integration","Hey Reach","project wrap-up"],"overview":"- **Data Handover**: Colin will send a Google Drive folder with engagement data and technologies to Edwin this week.  \n- **Tool Transition**: Edwin will focus on list building and outreach using available tools, confirming which will no longer be used.  \n- **Campaign Pause**: The team decided to pause HeyRich campaigns due to inactivity, reducing unnecessary costs and effort.  \n- **Cost-effective Options**: Colin recommended using Clay’s free tier for list building to support Edwin independently moving forward.  \n- **Positive Collaboration**: Both sides expressed goodwill and support during the transition, maintaining professional rapport despite project changes.  \n- **Handoff Timeline**: Colin will deliver project materials promptly, while Edwin verifies access to forms and addresses any issues.","action_items":"\n**Colin Costigan**\nPackage and send the Google Drive folder with all engagement materials and lists to Edwin (06:41)\nPrepare and share a list of all technologies used and those being sunset, including Smart Lead details (06:56)\nSend a zip file containing project files during the week (09:31)\nProvide a comprehensive list of tools including Clay and their uses (08:43)\n\n**Edwin Huertas**\nContinue testing and verifying access to web assets and tools (05:52)\nReach out to Colin via Slack as needed for list acquisition support during the next two weeks (07:18)\nPause use of Hey Reach campaigns until further notice (09:00)\nManage form submission follow-ups with updated contact info (08:29)\n"},"duration":10.880000114440918,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"id":1,"name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"id":2,"name":"Colin Costigan"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Hello?","index":0,"end_time":236.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":236.25,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Hello?","index":1,"end_time":237.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":236.73,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"It.","index":2,"end_time":255.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":255.46,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Hey, Edwin.","index":3,"end_time":295.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":294.59,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"I can''t hear you for some reason.","index":4,"end_time":298.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":297.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"There you are.","index":5,"end_time":314.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":313.72,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"There you go.","index":6,"end_time":315.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":314.52,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Yeah, Something changing my.","index":7,"end_time":317.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":315.16,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"My settings.","index":8,"end_time":318.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":317.48,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Hey, Nina, good morning.","index":9,"end_time":319.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":318.36,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"How things going with you?","index":10,"end_time":324.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":323.16,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"I don''t know if we''re gonna have anybody else.","index":11,"end_time":326.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":324.24,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"I don''t know if Mr. Is gonna join.","index":12,"end_time":327.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":326.04,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Kai is definitely not joining.","index":13,"end_time":328.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":327.32,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"So it''s gonna be hopefully not just me, but just me for now.","index":14,"end_time":333.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":328.76,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":15,"end_time":334.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":333.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, Misty accepted, but yeah, I haven''t seen her join yet.","index":16,"end_time":338.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":334.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But yeah, I mean just, just a wrap up meeting to see if there''s any follow up from your end, you know, if you want Smart Lead accounts or anything like that.","index":17,"end_time":347.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":340.11,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And that''s.","index":18,"end_time":349.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":348.59,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s pretty much where we''re at really.","index":19,"end_time":351.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":349.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I guess I was hoping for an.","index":20,"end_time":354.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":352.11,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Email or some sort of a checklist.","index":21,"end_time":356.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":354.23,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Not, not that I mentioned last.","index":22,"end_time":358.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":356.95,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"It just came to my mind that do I have everything in place?","index":23,"end_time":361.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":358.71,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Web stuff, the website, access.","index":24,"end_time":366.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":363.47,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"I just checked yesterday before.","index":25,"end_time":368.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":366.27,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Yes.","index":26,"end_time":368.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":368.07,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Just I have access.","index":27,"end_time":369.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":368.31,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"I''ve been like, do I have access to this?","index":28,"end_time":370.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":369.03,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Do I have access to this?","index":29,"end_time":371.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":370.47,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"You know, that''s what I''ve been going through.","index":30,"end_time":372.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":371.39,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"And I''m not sure if I''m missing something.","index":31,"end_time":374.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":372.91,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"I''m not sure if there''s anything else I should be getting access to.","index":32,"end_time":377.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":374.47,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"And that''s one and two, what I''m not going to get access to.","index":33,"end_time":380.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":377.55,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Like I know hay Rich is going to go away.","index":34,"end_time":382.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":380.43,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"I know these other tools we''re not.","index":35,"end_time":384.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":382.75,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Going to have access to.","index":36,"end_time":385.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":384.07,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"That''s one.","index":37,"end_time":386.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":386.11,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"And the reason I was getting access, like can I expand something?","index":38,"end_time":389.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":386.71,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Like can I get started getting exporting stuff?","index":39,"end_time":392.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":390.08,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"And then of course it came by, oh, I need the lists that we talked last time.","index":40,"end_time":398.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":394.08,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"I don''t know if you send it.","index":41,"end_time":399.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":398.52,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Or I looked into your polls, but.","index":42,"end_time":402.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":399.56,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"They were not lists or any of anything specifically of.","index":43,"end_time":406.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":402.28,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":44,"end_time":406.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":406.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So yeah.","index":45,"end_time":408.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":406.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So what we can do there is just is package up like the Google Drive folder that we have for everything we''ve done for our engagement and that''ll contain lists.","index":46,"end_time":415.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":408.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, good.","index":47,"end_time":416.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":416.24,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":48,"end_time":418.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":418.24,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then I can send just a list of like all of the technologies we''ve used and then.","index":49,"end_time":423.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":418.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, the ones that''ll be sunsetting, which will pretty much be.","index":50,"end_time":428.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":425.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Unless you want to move forward with Smart Lead.","index":51,"end_time":430.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":428.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think that''s pretty much everything as being sunset.","index":52,"end_time":432.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":430.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"This is more or less the only one.","index":53,"end_time":434.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":432.8,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Okay.","index":54,"end_time":434.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":434.12,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"That was the only one you were still making a decision on.","index":55,"end_time":437.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":435.28,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":56,"end_time":438.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":438.32,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"I don''t think.","index":57,"end_time":439.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":438.64,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":58,"end_time":439.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":439.2,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Yes.","index":59,"end_time":441.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":440.72,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"I don''t have an actual plan plan of how we''re gonna get lists.","index":60,"end_time":444.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":441.12,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"I might bother you a couple times here and there.","index":61,"end_time":447.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":445.08,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"The next two Weeks where I''m like, okay, who do I get lists from?","index":62,"end_time":450.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":447.92,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"And, you know, I''ll make.","index":63,"end_time":452.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":450.68,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"I''m still gonna be working.","index":64,"end_time":453.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":452.08,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"I''m pretty sure you guys are gonna.","index":65,"end_time":455.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":453.8,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Be working or not anymore.","index":66,"end_time":456.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":455.16,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"It''s kind of a mixed bag throughout the office.","index":67,"end_time":459.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":457.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":68,"end_time":460.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":459.64,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":69,"end_time":461.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":460.84,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Well, I''ll be sending stuff over slack in the next week.","index":70,"end_time":464.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":461.32,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"No problem at all to go through any of that.","index":71,"end_time":466.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":465.08,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":72,"end_time":467.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":467.56,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"So that list will help me a lot.","index":73,"end_time":469.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":467.92,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"So I know another domains for Smart.","index":74,"end_time":472.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":469.77,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Lead is one of the things I.","index":75,"end_time":473.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":472.33,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Wanted to use, but I was able to find another.","index":76,"end_time":475.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":473.77,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Another option, so.","index":77,"end_time":476.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":475.61,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Okay.","index":78,"end_time":477.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":476.97,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Or another email thing that I have.","index":79,"end_time":479.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":477.49,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"So I don''t think it''s that important anymore.","index":80,"end_time":482.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":480.09,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Gotcha.","index":81,"end_time":483.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":482.89,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Yeah, no, that''s all I needed.","index":82,"end_time":485.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":484.17,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Anything that you think I should have.","index":83,"end_time":487.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":485.93,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Access and I need to get access to and.","index":84,"end_time":491.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":487.65,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":85,"end_time":492.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":491.81,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"And have spot everything that I found out.","index":86,"end_time":494.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":492.13,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"I tested some form submissions.","index":87,"end_time":497.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":494.33,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"I couldn''t get him.","index":88,"end_time":499.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":498.6,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"And I figured, you know, something happened.","index":89,"end_time":501.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":499.52,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Yes, of course those email addresses are.","index":90,"end_time":503.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":501.32,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Not anymore.","index":91,"end_time":503.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":503.04,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"So thank you, Nina, for making that change.","index":92,"end_time":506.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":503.72,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"That helps.","index":93,"end_time":506.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":506.08,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"But I went through that list of.","index":94,"end_time":508.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":507,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"People submitting forms anyway, so there was not.","index":95,"end_time":510.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":508.68,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Not much.","index":96,"end_time":511.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":510.96,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Other than the one that already follow up.","index":97,"end_time":513,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":511.44,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":98,"end_time":513.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":513.32,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"So not much going on.","index":99,"end_time":515.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":513.72,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Gotcha.","index":100,"end_time":516.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":515.72,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":101,"end_time":516.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":516.36,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Well, yeah, I mean, we can package up the zip file and share that as well as a list of tools.","index":102,"end_time":521.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":516.76,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, we use Clay for list building.","index":103,"end_time":524.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":522.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m not sure if you''ve explored that at all.","index":104,"end_time":526.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":524.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"They do have a free T. Okay.","index":105,"end_time":528.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":526.16,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So there''s some things that you can do there.","index":106,"end_time":530.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":528.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But yeah, happy to answer any questions.","index":107,"end_time":531.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":530.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Of course.","index":108,"end_time":531.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":531.66,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"The other one is Heyrich.","index":109,"end_time":533.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":531.94,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"So that''s still going.","index":110,"end_time":534.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":533.22,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"I''m still getting people send invitations.","index":111,"end_time":536.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":534.18,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":112,"end_time":537.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":537.06,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So do you want me to.","index":113,"end_time":538.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":537.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Do you want us to pause that right now?","index":114,"end_time":539.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":538.1,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Sure.","index":115,"end_time":540.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":540.66,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"If we''re not using that one.","index":116,"end_time":542.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":540.98,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Yeah, I know there is.","index":117,"end_time":543.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":542.46,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"I know I have an account with them.","index":118,"end_time":544.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":543.26,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"The process is you get the list.","index":119,"end_time":547.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":545.62,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Of people you find somewhere and then you go to Hitreach to connect to LinkedIn.","index":120,"end_time":552.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":547.54,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Is that how it works?","index":121,"end_time":553.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":552.3,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":122,"end_time":553.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":553.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we can actually directly integrate Clay and Hay Reach.","index":123,"end_time":556.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":553.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we have the list that we build in clay.","index":124,"end_time":558.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":556.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"There''s actually one of the enrichments they have is just to add that to a campaign in heyreach.","index":125,"end_time":563.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":558.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, got it.","index":126,"end_time":564.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":563.79,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"And it will figure out who.","index":127,"end_time":566.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":564.75,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":128,"end_time":566.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":566.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You pick the campaign and then it maps like first name, last name, company, all that sort of stuff.","index":129,"end_time":570.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":566.75,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Got it.","index":130,"end_time":571.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":571.15,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":131,"end_time":572.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":571.79,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s all I have.","index":132,"end_time":574.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":572.75,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":133,"end_time":574.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":574.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, well, I''ll send over a list of tools.","index":134,"end_time":576.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":574.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''ll work on that.","index":135,"end_time":577.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":576.83,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then packaging up the zip file.","index":136,"end_time":581.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":579.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I won''t have all of it ready today.","index":137,"end_time":582.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":581.2,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But yeah, I''ll share that with you this week.","index":138,"end_time":585.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":583.88,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And I mean other than that, Edwin, it''s been an absolute pleasure working with.","index":139,"end_time":590.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":585.72,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You.","index":140,"end_time":591.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":590.84,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Know, it''s been a great relationship.","index":141,"end_time":594.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":593.32,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Wish we could drive more results but, you know, wishing Shaka the absolute best in your journey and you know, hoping that maybe this isn''t the last time we cross paths.","index":142,"end_time":605.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":595.08,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, same here.","index":143,"end_time":606.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":605.93,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"No, this has been great.","index":144,"end_time":607.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":606.61,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"I wish I was involved from the beginning.","index":145,"end_time":609.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":607.61,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"It would have been a completely different experience for us too.","index":146,"end_time":613.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":609.53,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"I think we did what we did and I think it''s, you know, depends of probably something.","index":147,"end_time":619.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":614.17,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Something else could have been done content wise, strategy wise.","index":148,"end_time":623.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":619.77,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"But no, I think they worked itself is good.","index":149,"end_time":625.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":623.49,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"I''m really excited, happy.","index":150,"end_time":627.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":625.85,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"I''m not sure what''s going to happen.","index":151,"end_time":628.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":627.69,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Next, but yes, if there''s a need.","index":152,"end_time":631.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":628.85,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"I know who to go to now.","index":153,"end_time":632.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":631.61,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Yeah, absolutely.","index":154,"end_time":634.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":633.25,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And your mom is still my prayers.","index":155,"end_time":637.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":634.17,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So best with all of that as well.","index":156,"end_time":640.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":637.45,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And a very merry Christmas.","index":157,"end_time":642.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":640.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Same to you.","index":158,"end_time":643.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":642.61,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Same to you, Nina.","index":159,"end_time":644.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":643.41,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Hope to see you soon Christmas.","index":160,"end_time":645.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":644.45,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"Bye.","index":161,"end_time":646.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":645.93,"speaker_name":"Edwin Huertas"},{"text":"All right.","index":162,"end_time":647.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":646.45,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Bye, Edwin.","index":163,"end_time":647.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":647.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"}],"dateString":"2025-12-23T16:00:00.000Z","host_email":"colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/88965765122?pwd=mPL1aFvxXYMYFRYawSa6f5Ez7s5Uv6.1","participants":["kylee.anger@shockoe.com,colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com,edwin@shockoe.com,misty.smith@shockoe.com,nina.belina@marketersindemand.com","kylee.anger@shockoe.com","edwin@shockoe.com","misty.smith@shockoe.com","nina.belina@marketersindemand.com"],"transcript_url":"https://app.fireflies.ai/view/01KCS81BFRNGTNE3C6N3RMXXVG","organizer_email":"colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com"}'::jsonb,
