  '[{"text":"Build detailed website project timeline slides including key milestones, assumptions (e.g., revision limits, scope boundaries), and dependencies based on copy delivery by January 2 (00:09)","completed":false},{"text":"Use provided kitchen sink template as a starting point to format timeline and milestone presentation slides (00:25)","completed":false},{"text":"Follow up with Kylie regarding status and delivery plan of copy for second ebook and remaining web pages to confirm drip-feed schedule (00:06)","completed":false},{"text":"Set up Slack channel for Encamp project team and client stakeholders; introduce Bailey and connect agency and client teams for streamlined communications (00:15)","completed":false},{"text":"Send the timeline and assumptions slide deck through Slack to client team once completed (00:17)","completed":false},{"text":"Manage scope creep by communicating clearly with client on out-of-scope items such as PowerPoint/social media templates, reinforce brand guidelines finality (00:05)","completed":false},{"text":"Engage closely with Nina and client’s Jenny B. and Kylie for project continuity and account management transition (00:01)","completed":false},{"text":"Coordinate with client’s content migration lead (Demir) to plan content export/import for blogs and knowledge articles using programmatic methods, assisted by AI tools (00:12)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
