  '[{"text":"Continue weekly ABM campaign monitoring and update shared documents with new responses (03:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Work with developers to improve email send rates without risking LinkedIn personal account blacklisting (03:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Prepare new ABM messaging campaign options with conversational/offer-style sequences for January presentation (04:30)","completed":false},{"text":"Share detailed ABM messaging sequences organized by audience group with Lauren, including contact lists (14:40)","completed":false},{"text":"Coordinate with designer Lou and submit ABM ads for Roderick''s final approval by December 23, then prepare for Stella''s review (19:30)","completed":false},{"text":"Add email open and click rate metrics with explanation of data accuracy to weekly reports (21:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Extend January meeting to 1 hour for strategic goal setting and planning (23:30)","completed":false},{"text":"Discuss lead qualification definitions with Bailey to align on lead handoff criteria and reporting (26:30)","completed":false},{"text":"Liaise with leadership regarding contract extension request to April and communicate response by early January (31:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Verify video project status and point allocations with internal team, delaying further edits until budget approval (42:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Send meeting recap and updated deliverables to Lauren and her team (50:45)","completed":false},{"text":"Review shared ABM messaging sequences and collaborate with Jay to refine target audiences and messaging per group (13:50)","completed":false},{"text":"Identify 20-50 top university targets for a potential limited offer campaign focusing on demos or consultations (16:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Share latest video edits comments with Taylor but hold off on further execution pending budget clarity (41:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Discuss contract extension and budgeting internally and provide feedback in early January (32:00)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
