    793,
    'https://us02web.zoom.us/j/88927304763?pwd=asbbQolEtVpMuYX5uccJpOibhnlog1.1',
    '{"id":"01KCHFSBXKWM9CBA4NPFA5ZXKY","title":"New North x Sedra Solutions: Weekly Meeting","summary":{"notes":"## **Marketing Performance and Campaign Updates**\n\nThe team reviewed recent marketing efforts showing steady engagement growth and outlined plans to refresh campaigns in the new year.\n\n- **Since launching two new email and LinkedIn Engagement Marketing (LEM) combos, 780 emails have been sent with no new responses expected due to seasonality** (09:16)  \n    - Taylor emphasized low activity is normal for late December and will monitor into January for changes  \n    - Organic social media gained **117 new followers** on the main page and **524 new followers** on Fahad''s page via the ABM campaign, signaling strong growth potential  \n    - Continued consistent organic content is key to sustaining follower growth and engagement in 2026  \n    - The paid video ads reached **10,679 views** and nearly **30,000 impressions**, indicating good brand exposure but needing stronger call-to-action results  \n\n- **The ABM campaign was adjusted with a fresh contact list last Thursday to push demo scheduling via targeted ads** (05:48)  \n    - New campaigns focus on encouraging direct demo clicks rather than just landing page visits  \n    - Ads are warming up to target audiences with similar job titles to broaden reach  \n    - Taylor projected improved demo conversion rates starting early 2026 as campaigns ramp up  \n    - The plan includes swapping the current video ad with the newly approved procurement video to refresh messaging and test engagement impact  \n\n- **Technical update required: Jeffrey needs to be added to the ad notification system manually since the team cannot do it on their side** (04:45)  \n    - Taylor sent instructions to Fahad for account ownership action to enable automatic lead notifications  \n    - This step is critical to maintaining timely lead follow-up and response  \n\n## **Sales Pipeline and Business Development Efforts**\n\nFahad outlined ongoing strategic sales efforts focusing on multiple entry points despite losing a key prospect.\n\n- **The M Group contract was lost to a competitor, Boy Shiller, but alternative leads remain active** (06:49)  \n    - Fahad stressed the M Group loss is a setback but not the end of pursuit  \n    - He is meeting tomorrow with the CEO of a company tied to a $1.6 billion fund that is creditor-related, aiming to demo the product and gain access to Brown Rudnick, the lawyers handling the case (07:22)  \n    - This meeting represents a critical opportunity to break into a lucrative referral network despite previous setbacks  \n    - Fahad showed strong commitment to exploring all angles and leveraging proof-of-concept work done over summer to maintain momentum  \n\n- **The team agreed to wait for Fahad’s feedback post-meeting before adjusting sales outreach strategy or offers** (08:15)  \n    - Taylor emphasized readiness to pivot based on Fahad’s insights and new opportunities  \n    - Refining demo offers remains a priority to increase conversion from the ABM campaign leads  \n\n## **Messaging and Brand Tone Adjustments**\n\nFeedback on message tone prompted a quick change to better align with professional standards and cultural expectations.\n\n- **Fahad requested changing LinkedIn outreach message greetings from “hey” to “hello” due to professionalism concerns** (09:27)  \n    - Taylor explained the original casual tone aims to reduce sales pitch perception based on ABM best practices  \n    - They agreed to switch to “hello” to maintain authenticity and respect Fahad’s style without losing conversational tone  \n    - This change will be implemented immediately by the developer managing the ABM campaign  \n    - Jackie reinforced the importance of authentic messaging to build trust with prospects (10:45)  \n\n## **Content Development and Timeline for Early 2026**\n\nContent plans focus on preparing a new ebook and brainstorming creative marketing ideas early next year.\n\n- **Jackie shared the first draft of the 2026 white collar trends ebook and requested Fahad’s feedback by the week of December 29** (11:59)  \n    - Fahad agreed to review within the week, aligning with Jackie’s planned leave the following week  \n    - The goal is to finalize and launch the ebook in early January to support thought leadership and lead generation efforts  \n\n- **The team planned to cancel the December 31 meeting and reconvene January 7 to strategize 2026 marketing plans** (05:48)  \n    - Discussion topics include exploring a comedy-style video and fresh campaign angles to increase demo conversion  \n    - Taylor emphasized learning from current analytics to avoid stagnation and keep content relevant through iterative testing  \n\n## **Operational and Process Notes**\n\nSmall process clarifications and maintenance tasks were addressed to improve campaign management and communication.\n\n- **Adding Jeffrey to the notification system requires Fahad’s direct account access to ensure lead alerts continue uninterrupted** (04:45)  \n    - This maintains accountability and quick sales response times for inbound leads  \n\n- **The team will monitor the impact of new email and ad campaigns closely in January to assess engagement and conversion lift** (09:16)  \n    - Adjustments will be made based on early data trends to optimize messaging and targeting  \n\n- **Taylor confirmed ongoing Slack communication for updates and coordination as the year closes** (11:50)  \n    - This keeps momentum during holiday season with minimal disruption  \n\n- **The team emphasized maintaining authenticity and cultural fit in outreach messaging to preserve brand reputation and engagement quality** (10:45)","outline":null,"keywords":["Procurement Video","ABM Campaign","LinkedIn Messaging","Organic Social Growth","Demo Scheduling","White Collar Trends eBook"],"overview":"- **Marketing Engagement Growth:** Recent marketing efforts show a steady increase in engagement, with 780 emails sent, 10,679 video views, and 641 new social media followers.\n- **Campaign Refresh Plans:** New ABM campaigns will focus on demo clicks, targeting specific job titles to enhance audience reach in early 2026.\n- **Sales Opportunity Following Loss:** Despite losing the M Group contract, a meeting with CEO tied to a $1.6 billion fund presents a potential new referral network.\n- **Tone of Outreach Messages:** LinkedIn outreach will shift from \"hey\" to \"hello\" to enhance professionalism while retaining a conversational style.\n- **Content Development Timeline:** A white collar trends ebook draft is due by December 29, with an aim to launch in January 2026 for lead generation.  \n- **Operational Updates:** Jeffrey needs manual addition to the notification system; the team will closely monitor campaign impact post-holiday.","action_items":"\n**Taylor Doerbaum**\nSend notification to team when new captioned procurement video version is live on the website (03:05)\nRequest developer to change LinkedIn ABM message greetings from “hey” to “hello” to address cultural concerns (10:45)\nCancel New Year’s Eve meeting and confirm January 7, 2026, as next meeting date (05:35)\nPrepare new video ad content using the updated procurement video and write fresh copy to refresh ads in early 2026 (08:30)\n\n**Jackie Wheeler**\nProvide feedback on the draft eBook about 2026 white collar trends by early January to proceed to production (11:57)\n\n**Fahad Al Mutawa**\nReview and provide feedback on the 2026 white collar trends eBook draft within the week (12:20)\nProceed with demo meeting with CEO of the $1.6 billion fund company tomorrow and explore opportunities with creditor law firms (07:43)\n"},"duration":13.210000038146973,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"id":1,"name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"id":2,"name":"Jackie Wheeler"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Good morning.","index":0,"end_time":7.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":6.56,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I just turned it off.","index":1,"end_time":9.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":8.16,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Hi.","index":2,"end_time":9.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":9.44,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"How are you doing?","index":3,"end_time":11.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":10.56,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Good, how are you?","index":4,"end_time":12.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":11.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Good.","index":5,"end_time":13.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":13.2,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Just getting everything ready for Christmas.","index":6,"end_time":15.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":13.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, this weekend was productive.","index":7,"end_time":17.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":15.84,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Are you a proactive shopper or a last minute shopper?","index":8,"end_time":21.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":17.92,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''m a proactive shopper.","index":9,"end_time":22.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":21.12,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I started in October, but.","index":10,"end_time":24.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":22.36,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Oh, wow.","index":11,"end_time":25.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":24.72,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We''re having our celebration tonight actually, because we''re heading out of town on Saturday, so.","index":12,"end_time":31.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":26.02,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah, like, I''m excited.","index":13,"end_time":33.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":31.7,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":14,"end_time":34.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":33.86,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That is fun.","index":15,"end_time":35.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":34.3,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":16,"end_time":35.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":35.1,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''m usually very last minute, but my husband and I are hosting my family from New York and everything this year, so.","index":17,"end_time":41.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":35.42,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Had to be on top of it.","index":18,"end_time":43.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":42.02,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":19,"end_time":44.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":43.94,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, it was like, oh, gosh.","index":20,"end_time":46.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":44.82,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yesterday I was like, oh, my gosh, I gotta wrap the presents today because everyone''s coming tomorrow.","index":21,"end_time":50.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":46.26,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So are you guys traveling somewhere fun for Christmas?","index":22,"end_time":53.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":50.18,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We''re going to Death Valley and then to Joshua Tree to just check those out and then, then landing and we''re gonna end up at Drew''s dad for Christmas Eve and his mom''s for Christmas Day, so.","index":23,"end_time":64.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":53.1,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Nice.","index":24,"end_time":65.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":64.72,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Are you guys like rv, RV people, or do you camp?","index":25,"end_time":68.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":65.16,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Okay.","index":26,"end_time":68.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":68.32,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, we''ve got a camper van, so.","index":27,"end_time":71.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":68.8,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s great.","index":28,"end_time":72.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":71.52,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"We love it.","index":29,"end_time":72.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":72.24,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yes.","index":30,"end_time":73.879,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":73.44,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"My husband wants me to like, camp on the ground with him whenever we.","index":31,"end_time":76.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":73.879,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"He has that idea because he was big into that growing up and my family were hotel people.","index":32,"end_time":81.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":76.96,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"RVs are a really good compromise.","index":33,"end_time":85.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":83.6,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I was always a tech person too, but armies are a great compromise.","index":34,"end_time":89.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":85.24,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Tell them.","index":35,"end_time":90.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":89.82,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I''m like, if you give me like shelter, like an actual structure, I''ll think about it.","index":36,"end_time":94.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":90.02,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But like, the national parks would be cool to do.","index":37,"end_time":97.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":94.94,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Oh, it''s fantastic.","index":38,"end_time":98.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":97.34,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"And it''s great because, you know, you.","index":39,"end_time":100.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":98.82,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"We, we went to Yellowstone earlier this year and Grand Teton and stuff.","index":40,"end_time":103.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":100.7,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"And we had our RV so in the morning, it would be like 4:30 in the morning and we wanted to get out early to where the wolves were and stuff and see them.","index":41,"end_time":111.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":103.98,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"We didn''t see wolves, but.","index":42,"end_time":112.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":111.34,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"And we just pack up and go and we take our camper with us and then we make coffee and then we, you know, we had breakfast and then I was tired, so I took a little nap while we''re waiting to see more bison come.","index":43,"end_time":121.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":113.18,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"And it''s.","index":44,"end_time":122.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":121.88,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"It''s fantastic having your little mobile home with you everywhere.","index":45,"end_time":125.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":122.72,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"It''s amazing.","index":46,"end_time":126.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":125.92,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah, Yeah, I would be about that.","index":47,"end_time":129,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":127.32,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''m not about the on the ground camping.","index":48,"end_time":131.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":129,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, I, I''m over that.","index":49,"end_time":132.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":131.56,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah, I''m totally over it.","index":50,"end_time":134.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":132.92,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yes.","index":51,"end_time":135.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":135.4,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''ll have to.","index":52,"end_time":136.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":135.88,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''ll have to let him know.","index":53,"end_time":137.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":136.44,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I told him I''d camp with him more if if that was the situation.","index":54,"end_time":140.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":137.28,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But I don''t like the idea of sleeping on the ground.","index":55,"end_time":142.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":140.12,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And I don''t know if a bear could come maul you in the middle of the night because you''re in a test.","index":56,"end_time":147.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":142.96,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Talking about tent camping versus RV camping.","index":57,"end_time":154.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":151.23,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Oh, yes.","index":58,"end_time":156.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":154.67,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":59,"end_time":158.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":157.95,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I prefer hotel camping.","index":60,"end_time":160.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":158.91,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Neither work for me.","index":61,"end_time":161.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":160.23,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"That''s what I was saying.","index":62,"end_time":161.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":161.07,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''m from a family of.","index":63,"end_time":162.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":161.83,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We do hotels and my husband comes from camping, so hotels are better.","index":64,"end_time":169.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":163.07,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I agree.","index":65,"end_time":170.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":169.71,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":66,"end_time":173.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":172.83,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Let me pull up our agenda here.","index":67,"end_time":175.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":173.43,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We don''t have too much need to go over with you as we wrap up the year, which is crazy.","index":68,"end_time":180.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":175.19,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But we have that new procurement video.","index":69,"end_time":183.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":180.45,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"All those versions are approved.","index":70,"end_time":184.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":183.33,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So thank you for that.","index":71,"end_time":185.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":184.61,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And we''re going to go ahead and add that caption version to the website and replace where that procurement screenshot is that you sent Jackie.","index":72,"end_time":191.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":185.37,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So as soon as that''s live, I will send that over to you.","index":73,"end_time":194.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":191.45,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":74,"end_time":195.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":194.77,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Thank you so much.","index":75,"end_time":196.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":195.29,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yes.","index":76,"end_time":196.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":196.37,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then we have.","index":77,"end_time":197.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":196.81,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We''re up to 780 emails have been sent since we launched those two new combos of the emails and LEM lists.","index":78,"end_time":205.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":197.49,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we''ll continue to keep an eye on that.","index":79,"end_time":206.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":205.38,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We haven''t seen any new responses come in, but that makes sense for the time of year right now.","index":80,"end_time":210.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":206.9,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"A lot of people aren''t looking for that at the moment.","index":81,"end_time":213.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":210.62,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then I went through and I wanted to do a year in review of the organic social.","index":82,"end_time":219.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":214.46,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So for the main page, we gained 117 new followers, which is great.","index":83,"end_time":223.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":219.58,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"As long as we continue to keep that organic content consistent, we should see that continue to rise.","index":84,"end_time":228.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":223.26,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And since there wasn''t too much data to compare from the previous year, we don''t have any comparisons here yet.","index":85,"end_time":233.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":228.46,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But as we go into the next year, we will.","index":86,"end_time":235.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":233.1,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we had a good reach and engagements.","index":87,"end_time":237.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":235.22,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We''ll continue to monitor that in the new year.","index":88,"end_time":240.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":238.78,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then for Fahad''s page, because we have that ABM campaign rolling, we''ve seen a larger increase, so we have 524 new followers, which is great.","index":89,"end_time":248.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":240.62,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then also a high number of connections.","index":90,"end_time":251.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":248.98,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And again, we can compare the reach and engagements in the next year as we can have more data to support that.","index":91,"end_time":257.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":251.74,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But it''s really great to see that giant influx.","index":92,"end_time":260.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":257.1,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And as we continue to have that campaign running, we should see your followers increase.","index":93,"end_time":264.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":260.27,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So that is great.","index":94,"end_time":265.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":264.31,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We just got to keep that organic content up.","index":95,"end_time":267.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":265.91,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":96,"end_time":270.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":270.23,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then the paid ad updates.","index":97,"end_time":273.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":272.47,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I sent the directions.","index":98,"end_time":275.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":273.99,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Our team wasn''t able to add Jeffrey as the notification system.","index":99,"end_time":280.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":275.99,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I don''t know if you saw that.","index":100,"end_time":281.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":280.71,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So it just has to be done on your end since you''re the owner of the account.","index":101,"end_time":283.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":281.51,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But I sent those instructions so he can get those automatic notifications like you do.","index":102,"end_time":288.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":283.87,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But those leads come in that way continuously.","index":103,"end_time":293,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":290.52,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Nothing new there.","index":104,"end_time":293.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":293,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then the video ads, I wanted to go over a quarter review.","index":105,"end_time":297.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":294.28,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we have 10,679 views on that and almost nearly 30,000 impressions, which is great.","index":106,"end_time":303.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":297.72,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then the ABM ads also, we have a good amount of website visits here.","index":107,"end_time":309.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":303.96,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We obviously want to get it over the line to get that demo button hit.","index":108,"end_time":313.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":309.24,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then we also have high impressions.","index":109,"end_time":315.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":313.64,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And with the new ads that we implemented with that list you sent over last Thursday, that is a direct campaign to encourage a demo, whereas a couple of these were landing on whether it was the procurement data sheet and things like that.","index":110,"end_time":328.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":315.4,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So with this new campaign, we''re hoping it increases the amount of engagement to that page where we can have people actually get to the finish line of scheduling the demo.","index":111,"end_time":336.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":328.43,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we have the contacts that you sent us implemented in.","index":112,"end_time":339.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":336.67,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then it''s also warming up right now the ads to get people with similar job titles as well, so we can get more audience into those campaigns.","index":113,"end_time":348.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":339.71,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So that''ll be a good one to see in the new year, is that we''ll start to ramp up and warm up.","index":114,"end_time":354.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":348.35,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So now''s a good time to get that going.","index":115,"end_time":356.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":354.19,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But yeah, hoping to get more people to click the button instead of just landing on the page.","index":116,"end_time":361.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":356.35,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So going into 2026, I think that when we meet next, I assume we''re probably going to cancel New Year''s Eve meeting.","index":117,"end_time":372.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":364.27,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I just wanted to show, okay, some people are online, some people aren''t.","index":118,"end_time":376.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":372.63,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I''ll go ahead and cancel that one and then we''ll meet again on the 7th and maybe we could brainstorm some ideas of what we''re looking to do in 2026.","index":119,"end_time":385.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":376.99,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I know we had talked about doing another video, the.","index":120,"end_time":387.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":385.07,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The comedy style one if we wanted to explore that option and then just kind of the goals.","index":121,"end_time":392.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":387.83,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then also with the offer for the abm, we''ve sent a lot of things out, we''ve gotten close to one.","index":122,"end_time":398.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":393.15,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But obviously we want to kind of refine our offer and make it more compell, potentially get someone to schedule.","index":123,"end_time":405.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":398.99,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I know we''re pending a couple things.","index":124,"end_time":406.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":405.41,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I assume we don''t have an update on the mint group thing yet.","index":125,"end_time":409.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":406.85,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I don''t think they''re going to get it last.","index":126,"end_time":411.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":409.93,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Yeah, I think another firm got it.","index":127,"end_time":414.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":412.89,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Oh, no.","index":128,"end_time":416.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":415.37,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":129,"end_time":417.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":417.13,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But we still have our, you know, we''re still trying through these other Angles.","index":130,"end_time":420.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":417.49,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"So there''s multiple people.","index":131,"end_time":421.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":420.25,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Okay.","index":132,"end_time":422.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":422.33,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But the M Group would have been the easiest.","index":133,"end_time":424.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":422.77,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":134,"end_time":425.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":425.29,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But it''s a firm called Boy Shiller.","index":135,"end_time":428.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":426.73,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"It seems based on my recent search that they just got it.","index":136,"end_time":432.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":428.65,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"But we''re still trying to get while because we''ve done a proof of concept for them over the summer.","index":137,"end_time":439.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":433.3,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Who are the attorneys for the company itself.","index":138,"end_time":441.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":439.1,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Okay.","index":139,"end_time":442.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":441.54,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And we are meeting with.","index":140,"end_time":445.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":442.06,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Remember I told you guys last week, I know this company, one of the companies that part of the 1.6 billion dollar fund that invested or is part of the debtors to the company.","index":141,"end_time":460.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":445.94,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I have a meeting with them tomorrow.","index":142,"end_time":461.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":460.29,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Great.","index":143,"end_time":462.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":462.21,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Here in Kuwait.","index":144,"end_time":463.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":463.09,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"So I''m meeting with their CEO, demoing our product to him.","index":145,"end_time":467.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":463.85,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"If he buys into it, he might be our ticket into the lawyers that are dealing for the creditors, which is Brown Rudnick.","index":146,"end_time":477.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":467.81,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"So I don''t care how I get in.","index":147,"end_time":479.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":477.41,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":148,"end_time":479.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":479.17,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I''m looking at every single aspect.","index":149,"end_time":482.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":479.61,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"So I''m, you know, that''s why we''re pushing against all these things.","index":150,"end_time":484.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":482.09,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Okay.","index":151,"end_time":485.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":485.38,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Because it''s worth the fight and we''ll try our best.","index":152,"end_time":488.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":485.74,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Don''t know what''s going to happen, but we''ll keep, you know, keep on pushing.","index":153,"end_time":491.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":488.42,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":154,"end_time":492.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":492.1,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That''s good that there are some other avenues to explore then too.","index":155,"end_time":495.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":492.82,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And it wasn''t just that one.","index":156,"end_time":496.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":495.42,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":157,"end_time":497.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":496.74,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Great.","index":158,"end_time":497.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":497.3,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Well, we''ll wait to hear back from you on that then.","index":159,"end_time":499.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":497.62,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then we can kind of move forward with a new idea of how we can approach that.","index":160,"end_time":503.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":499.5,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But yeah, I think we''re in a good spot right now.","index":161,"end_time":505.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":503.06,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then with the new procurement video, I think there might be opportunity to update our ads because we''ve had the same video ad running.","index":162,"end_time":511.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":505.5,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I think it''d be good to switch that out since we''ve had that running for a while.","index":163,"end_time":514.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":511.7,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We can update it to the new procurement one if you guys like that idea.","index":164,"end_time":518.159,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":514.74,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And we could write some copy out for that and just switch out that video so we can refresh the ads from what we currently have, which was the original video we created back almost a year ago.","index":165,"end_time":528.559,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":518.879,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we can work on a couple of those ideas.","index":166,"end_time":532.718,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":530.479,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We can come prepared with some new ideas on different angles that we could take to increase that engagement.","index":167,"end_time":537.719,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":532.718,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Because, yeah, we want to make sure things don''t stay stagnant and we can keep up to date and learn from the analytics that we have seen so far.","index":168,"end_time":545.679,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":537.719,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So with those new emails running, it''ll be a good test to see if that makes a difference.","index":169,"end_time":550.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":546.96,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And again, it''s a tricky time of year right now at the end of December, but hopefully in the beginning of January, we can start seeing how we can change and alter a couple of things to increase engagement.","index":170,"end_time":561.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":550.64,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yes, and we''d love to hear from you guys too, if you have any other things coming up or events.","index":171,"end_time":567.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":563.36,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, I just have one small, small comment.","index":172,"end_time":570.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":567.72,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I was looking at my LinkedIn and I''m seeing the messages that are going from me to the connections and they start with hey, H e y and I just find it very strange.","index":173,"end_time":582.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":570.24,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"We can change that very easily.","index":174,"end_time":584.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":583.38,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I. I don''t know, maybe it''s a cultural thing or a language barrier, but it seems so unprofessional from my angle.","index":175,"end_time":593.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":585.22,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I mean, I never use hey, I just felt way out of character.","index":176,"end_time":598.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":593.82,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I''m not trying to be picky, but I don''t want to give the wrong impression.","index":177,"end_time":602.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":599.14,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"No, the reason.","index":178,"end_time":604.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":603.57,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So with LinkedIn versus email, the way we kind of structure it is with email, it''s more formal.","index":179,"end_time":610.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":604.85,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we always do like a formal greeting.","index":180,"end_time":612.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":610.77,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"With LinkedIn, a lot of like ABM stats show that if you''re too formal, then people automatically read that as a sales pitch.","index":181,"end_time":620.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":612.69,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So if you go at it from an informal angle, then it''s more like a conversation.","index":182,"end_time":624.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":620.01,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So that''s why we do that.","index":183,"end_time":625.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":624.45,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But just change it to high preference.","index":184,"end_time":627.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":625.53,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We can change it to high if that''s better.","index":185,"end_time":629.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":627.73,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But hi.","index":186,"end_time":630.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":630.34,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Hello.","index":187,"end_time":631.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":631.22,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Hello.","index":188,"end_time":633.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":632.58,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We could do it to hello too, but it''s totally fine.","index":189,"end_time":635.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":633.14,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Like if you were like, ah, this doesn''t.","index":190,"end_time":637.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":635.54,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s not like authentic to you, then we can definitely switch that.","index":191,"end_time":640.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":637.42,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we can even my emails, I use hello, so it''s, it''s very less.","index":192,"end_time":644.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":640.42,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, that''s a quick change.","index":193,"end_time":647.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":645.86,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''ll, I''ll get on that right after this.","index":194,"end_time":649.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":647.9,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''ll send it over to one of our developers who maintains and just checks on the maintenance of the ABM campaign.","index":195,"end_time":655.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":649.78,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''ll just ask him to switch those over to hello, but that''s totally fine.","index":196,"end_time":658.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":655.14,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But yeah, the reason we do it is so it''s more of a casual introduction instead of like a good afternoon, you know, hello.","index":197,"end_time":664.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":658.27,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But hello is hello is the same as hey, basically.","index":198,"end_time":667.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":664.71,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So it''s great feedback, Fahad.","index":199,"end_time":669.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":667.75,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"And anytime you see something that doesn''t land right with you, always, always, always tell us because it''s really important.","index":200,"end_time":676.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":669.67,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"The most important thing in today''s climate is that things come across as authentic.","index":201,"end_time":681.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":676.79,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So if something doesn''t sound authentically you, we want to change it.","index":202,"end_time":685.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":681.75,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So yeah, don''t, don''t hesitate to give that feedback.","index":203,"end_time":688.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":685.45,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"No, I was like, you know, I thought I''d wait till I talked to you.","index":204,"end_time":691.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":689.13,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"It wasn''t something urgent.","index":205,"end_time":692.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":691.85,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I was like, I never say.","index":206,"end_time":694.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":692.69,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Hey, That''s an easy.","index":207,"end_time":699.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":694.17,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Thanks.","index":208,"end_time":700.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":699.89,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That''s an easy thing.","index":209,"end_time":701.249,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":700.29,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We can switch that over to hello.","index":210,"end_time":702.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":701.249,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That''s funny.","index":211,"end_time":703.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":702.89,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, no, I''m glad you mentioned it.","index":212,"end_time":705.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":704.33,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, can change that around.","index":213,"end_time":708.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":705.93,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":214,"end_time":710.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":709.61,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Well, that''s everything I have for the rest of this year, but we''ll.","index":215,"end_time":713.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":710.33,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We''ll keep in touch on Slack and I''ll send any updates that I have there, but I hope you guys have.","index":216,"end_time":718.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":713.56,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Well, one.","index":217,"end_time":719.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":719.08,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"One other thing.","index":218,"end_time":720.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":719.68,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So I''ve got the.","index":219,"end_time":721.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":720.76,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"The ebook.","index":220,"end_time":722.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":721.76,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"The first draft of the ebook, about 2026 white collar trends.","index":221,"end_time":726.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":722.92,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Fahad, I sent that to you and.","index":222,"end_time":727.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":726.6,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"And us.","index":223,"end_time":728.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":727.84,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So when you get around to it, I''d love to get your feedback on it so we can get that into production and ready to hit the ground at the beginning of January, if possible.","index":224,"end_time":737.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":728.6,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Sure, I''ll try to get to it this week.","index":225,"end_time":740.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":738.57,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Okay, perfect.","index":226,"end_time":741.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":740.65,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I''ll be out next week, so you''ve got time.","index":227,"end_time":743.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":741.77,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"But I''ll be back online Monday the 29th, so you''ve got.","index":228,"end_time":749.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":744.57,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"You''ve got a week to deal with.","index":229,"end_time":751.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":749.93,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"It, so no problem.","index":230,"end_time":752.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":751.01,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Okay, that''ll be great.","index":231,"end_time":754.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":753.21,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Have a happy new Year.","index":232,"end_time":756.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":754.89,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Enjoy your holidays.","index":233,"end_time":757.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":756.09,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":234,"end_time":758.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":758.17,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Same to all of you.","index":235,"end_time":760.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":759.21,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Better than camping.","index":236,"end_time":761.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":760.41,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I agree.","index":237,"end_time":763.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":762.73,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I agree.","index":238,"end_time":763.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":763.29,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Kevin is going camping, Jackie.","index":239,"end_time":766.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":764.97,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Oh, yeah, yeah, yeah, he''s going camping.","index":240,"end_time":770.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":767.69,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"I think first few days of January.","index":241,"end_time":772.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":770.21,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Nice with him.","index":242,"end_time":774.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":772.65,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"And, you know, camping seems to be the theme.","index":243,"end_time":776.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":774.13,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"It''s what we love to do, especially in California.","index":244,"end_time":779.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":777.05,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"We have great camping here, so.","index":245,"end_time":781.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":779.77,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"No, enjoy.","index":246,"end_time":783.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":782.73,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Of course you do.","index":247,"end_time":784.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":783.41,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Yeah, enjoy.","index":248,"end_time":784.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":784.13,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":249,"end_time":785.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":785.13,"speaker_name":"fahad al mutawa"},{"text":"All right, Happy holidays.","index":250,"end_time":786.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":785.57,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Bye, everyone.","index":251,"end_time":787.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":786.65,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"}],"dateString":"2025-12-17T16:30:00.000Z","host_email":"taylor.doerbaum@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/88927304763?pwd=asbbQolEtVpMuYX5uccJpOibhnlog1.1","participants":["taylor.doerbaum@marketersindemand.com,baylee.gunnell@marketersindemand.com,j.wheeler@sedrasolutions.com,i.hamshari@sedrasolutions.com,f.almutawa@sedrasolutions.com","baylee.gunnell@marketersindemand.com","j.wheeler@sedrasolutions.com","i.hamshari@sedrasolutions.com","f.almutawa@sedrasolutions.com"],"transcript_url":"https://app.fireflies.ai/view/01KCHFSBXKWM9CBA4NPFA5ZXKY","organizer_email":"taylor.doerbaum@marketersindemand.com"}'::jsonb,
