    '{"id":"01KCHTRXDD3A0AV6C2FG7Z6KJH","title":"Hydrian // New North: Weekly Meeting (new)","summary":{"notes":"## **Survey and Lead Generation Strategy**\n\nThe team agreed to launch the survey in early January with a focus on realistic lead expectations and clearer goal setting.\n\n- **Michael Jones confirmed the survey is ready to go live and suggested scheduling it for the second or third week of January to avoid holiday distractions** (25:06)  \n    - The survey is designed to send to all contacts within **48 hours**, consolidating results in one place for efficient analysis.  \n    - Michael emphasized the need to finalize the first five questions and structure the survey report with input from Josh.  \n    - They decided to hold off on expanding the contact list now due to duplicates and job title cleanup, planning to revisit after the new year.  \n    - The goal is to focus on achievable outcomes rather than unrealistic lead generation targets.\n\n- **Michael highlighted the absence of meaningful lead generation over the past four years with Hydra, urging a redefinition of the partnership’s purpose** (18:25)  \n    - He acknowledged successes in brand building and follower growth but stressed that lead generation has never met expectations.  \n    - Michael proposed focusing on realistic deliverables, reducing pressure around leads to better align efforts.  \n    - Taylor Doerbaum responded with ideas to ease content creation burdens and planned to bring fresh lead generation strategies in 2026.  \n    - They aim to integrate revamped ABM processes into new campaigns early next year to improve lead outcomes.\n\n## **Website and Conversion Optimization**\n\nFixing the website’s contact and assessment pages is the top priority to convert visitors into clients.\n\n- **Michael emphasized that getting the website contact and assessment pages fully functional would justify the entire engagement cost** (23:18)  \n    - Visitors frequently land on these pages but fail to convert, which is the biggest mystery affecting lead flow.  \n    - Once clients reach out by phone, conversion is nearly 100%, demonstrating a strong closing process post-contact.  \n    - The team agreed that improving user flow to encourage form completions or calls is the key pivot for success.  \n    - Taylor noted that short attention spans are a common barrier, confirming this is a widespread challenge across clients.\n\n## **Content and Newsletter Planning**\n\nThe team will shift the January newsletter focus to a light, engaging yearly recap instead of survey results.\n\n- **Taylor proposed a New Year’s newsletter highlighting 2025’s key moments and 2026 outlook, inspired by popular formats like Spotify Wrapped** (11:34)  \n    - Michael liked the idea of a lighthearted recap to engage contacts without heavy formal content.  \n    - The newsletter would set the tone for the year and tease upcoming survey insights scheduled for February.  \n    - This approach addresses current content creation challenges and eases workload by repurposing existing material.  \n    - It also aligns with audience preferences for relatable, less formal communications.\n\n- **Organic growth metrics showed positive momentum, with Josh gaining 338 new followers and 68 new connections in the past year** (17:19)  \n    - Hydrant also experienced increased follower engagement and reach, supporting ongoing content scheduling.  \n    - These gains validate the brand-building efforts, even as lead generation remains a challenge.  \n    - Maintaining this momentum is important for long-term engagement and visibility.\n\n## **Exhibition Booth Design and Budget**\n\nA preferred booth design was selected with plans to finalize approval after input from a key stakeholder.\n\n- **Michael identified the last design option as the strongest and plans to get final approval from Josh in mid-January** (06:05)  \n    - The chosen design balances visibility and aesthetic, especially accounting for the presence of a table or stool in front.  \n    - The booth cost is approximately **$3,000**, and Michael wants to avoid redesign costs of around **$700** by confirming the design upfront.  \n    - They agreed to finalize this booth first before redesigning the smaller stand booth later, accepting minor design inconsistencies between the two.  \n    - This staged approach manages budget and timing risks while ensuring brand consistency.\n\n## **Partnership Expectations and Operational Realism**\n\nThe discussion revealed a need to realign expectations between the firm and Hydra, focusing on achievable goals with no blame.\n\n- **Michael stressed the importance of setting realistic goals for 2026, particularly around lead generation, based on four years of experience** (19:10)  \n    - He acknowledged Hydra’s value in website, brand, and content support but noted internal barriers to adopting new ideas like video content.  \n    - Both parties agreed to maintain the partnership without blame, emphasizing transparency and practical targets.  \n    - Taylor committed to bringing new ideas to reduce client workload and enhance content output despite busy schedules.  \n    - Michael reinforced that clear expectations and honest conversations are the most productive way to work together going forward.\n\n- **Michael plans to share additional thoughts before the next meeting on December 28 to shape the 2026 strategy** (21:28)  \n    - The upcoming session aims to align all stakeholders on priorities and actionable plans.  \n    - This collaborative approach intends to improve clarity and focus throughout the year.  \n    - The team will prepare ideas and identify any additional discussion points ahead of time.","outline":null,"keywords":["Survey Launch","Booth Design","Lead Generation","Newsletter Strategy","Website Conversion","Content Creation"],"overview":"- **Survey Launch Planned:** Survey to go live in early January, focusing on realistic lead expectations and achievable goals.  \n- **Website Optimization Priority:** Fixing website contact and assessment pages is crucial for converting visitors into clients.  \n- **Newsletter Focus Shift:** January newsletter will provide a light recap of past year instead of survey results, easing content creation.  \n- **Booth Design Finalized:** Preferred booth design chosen, aiming for final approval by mid-January to manage costs and branding.  \n- **Realistic Partnership Goals:** Emphasis on setting achievable targets for 2026, maintaining a blame-free, transparent partnership approach.  \n- **Ongoing Engagement Metrics:** Positive growth noted with 338 new followers and 68 new connections, supporting brand-building efforts.","action_items":"\n**Michael Jones**\nSend design feedback and final approval for the booth to designer post-New Year, after consulting Josh (06:05)\nShare ideas and thoughts on realistic marketing goals and content before the 28th December meeting (20:50)\nEnsure website contact and assessment page is functioning optimally to convert visitors into clients, emphasize its priority (23:00)\n\n**Taylor Doerbaum**\nRemove phone box from free assessment as approved and launch it live (04:00)\nSchedule the survey to launch the second or third week of January (10:18)\nHold on expanding company list for survey until new year; plan to clean and enrich the list then (09:47)\nPrepare and propose a New Year''s themed newsletter for January as a 2025 recap and 2026 preview with a teaser for February’s survey insights (11:30)\nDevelop content gathering workarounds to ease client burden on content creation (21:30)\nPrepare for brainstorming session on 28th December with tailored ideas for marketing and lead generation strategy adjustments (22:36)\n\n**Unassigned**\nContinue scheduling and running the ABM process revamp to integrate new leads generation strategies (21:30)\n"},"duration":26.3700008392334,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Michael Jones"},{"id":1,"name":"Taylor Doerbaum"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Hello.","index":0,"end_time":7.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":7.52,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Hello.","index":1,"end_time":8.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":8.32,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"How are you doing?","index":2,"end_time":10.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":9.52,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"All right.","index":3,"end_time":11.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":10.8,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"How are you?","index":4,"end_time":11.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":11.28,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Good.","index":5,"end_time":13.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":12.64,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Ready for Christmas?","index":6,"end_time":14.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":13.52,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I think we are.","index":7,"end_time":17.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":16.32,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":8,"end_time":18.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":17.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I think it''s going to be a quiet one, to be honest with you.","index":9,"end_time":20.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":18.32,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"There''s only.","index":10,"end_time":21.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":20.72,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Well, it''s my wife and myself.","index":11,"end_time":22.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":21.52,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We sing our son Christmas Eve, I think Christmas Day, and that''s it.","index":12,"end_time":29.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":23.28,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So.","index":13,"end_time":30.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":30.13,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yes.","index":14,"end_time":31.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":30.53,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I don''t know about you guys.","index":15,"end_time":33.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":32.29,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Have you got lots of plans?","index":16,"end_time":35.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":33.57,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We''re hosting my family, actually, from New York, so we will have a full house.","index":17,"end_time":40.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":36.13,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And my brother and his fiance are driving from New York, so that''ll be far.","index":18,"end_time":45.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":40.45,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And they''re gonna bring their dog.","index":19,"end_time":46.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":45.33,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"They didn''t want to leave their dog, so they''ll have a long road trip.","index":20,"end_time":51.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":46.93,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But it''ll stand that know when we''ve got a dog.","index":21,"end_time":54.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":51.17,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And it''s sort of like, you know, we.","index":22,"end_time":55.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":54.1,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Everything we plan around is everything.","index":23,"end_time":57.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":55.54,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Like no more than four hours away from anything, you know.","index":24,"end_time":60.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":57.3,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Right.","index":25,"end_time":60.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":60.18,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Or out for the.","index":26,"end_time":61.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":60.66,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Out for the day is four hours maximum, you know, there and back.","index":27,"end_time":64.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":61.62,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yes, they understand that.","index":28,"end_time":68.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":66.58,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":29,"end_time":69.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":68.74,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So they''re bringing.","index":30,"end_time":70.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":69.22,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And we have a dog, too, and they''ve never met, so we''re.","index":31,"end_time":73.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":70.78,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"They''ll.","index":32,"end_time":74.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":74.26,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"They''ll have fun.","index":33,"end_time":75.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":74.74,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And it''s really warm here in Texas.","index":34,"end_time":77.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":75.5,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s in the 70s today, so they''re ready to.","index":35,"end_time":80.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":77.34,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That''s not bad, is it, the warm weather.","index":36,"end_time":82.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":80.42,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And it''s weird because we had like, insane cold weather the last few days, and now it''s.","index":37,"end_time":89.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":82.6,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It''s not too bad.","index":38,"end_time":89.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":89.12,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It''s like, gosh, what is it, 5 degrees centigrade?","index":39,"end_time":94.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":89.84,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So what is it now?","index":40,"end_time":95.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":94.2,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"40, 45 maybe?","index":41,"end_time":96.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":95.08,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Something like that.","index":42,"end_time":97.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":96.6,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Oh, yeah.","index":43,"end_time":98.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":97.639,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Not too bad.","index":44,"end_time":99.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":98.76,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":45,"end_time":100.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":100.12,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I heard you''re in Chicago, right?","index":46,"end_time":103,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":100.44,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yes, I heard that it was like five degrees or something the other day because.","index":47,"end_time":107.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":103.32,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And someone at, like the Bears game said it was like they''re.","index":48,"end_time":111.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":108.02,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"They opened their soda and it just like froze at the game outside.","index":49,"end_time":116.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":111.3,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Like, the second they cracked it, I was like, oh, man.","index":50,"end_time":118.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":116.42,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I know.","index":51,"end_time":119.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":119.06,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We were sort of like.","index":52,"end_time":120.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":119.62,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I think where we are, we''re in the suburbs, so we are 40 miles northeast of the.","index":53,"end_time":128.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":121.22,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Of Chicago itself.","index":54,"end_time":130.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":129.3,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I can''t.","index":55,"end_time":132.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":132.5,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I think we''re sort of east, not north, anyway.","index":56,"end_time":135.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":132.98,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":57,"end_time":136.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":136.2,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And it was sort of like, with the wind chill.","index":58,"end_time":138.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":136.76,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It was minus seven.","index":59,"end_time":139.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":138.72,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, that was a.","index":60,"end_time":141.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":140.2,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"That was the thing that was the most upsetting was like, it''s insane because it was the wind chill that was sort of cold, you know, sort of.","index":61,"end_time":147.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":141.96,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Hits you in the bones.","index":62,"end_time":148.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":147.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s just.","index":63,"end_time":148.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":148.36,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":64,"end_time":149.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":148.84,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And so we basically.","index":65,"end_time":150.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":149.16,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We finally went, okay, now it''s warm enough.","index":66,"end_time":152.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":150.52,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We went to get logs for the fireplace And I said, what should I get?","index":67,"end_time":157.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":153.24,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And she goes, right.","index":68,"end_time":158.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":157.92,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Everything we can get our hands on.","index":69,"end_time":160.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":158.84,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So we got three.","index":70,"end_time":160.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":160.36,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"300 logs, pieces of wood to, you know, so we''ve got enough firewood to keep going, keep the room, keep the house warm.","index":71,"end_time":169.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":161.08,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"That''s cold again.","index":72,"end_time":170.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":169.32,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"That''s good.","index":73,"end_time":172.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":171.4,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That''s very Christmassy.","index":74,"end_time":173.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":172.08,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That''s cozy.","index":75,"end_time":174.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":173.64,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That''s true.","index":76,"end_time":174.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":174.32,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yes.","index":77,"end_time":175.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":174.84,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"All the Christmas decorations are up.","index":78,"end_time":176.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":175.12,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We sort of.","index":79,"end_time":178.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":177.48,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I. I''m terrible for that.","index":80,"end_time":179.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":178.28,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I was like, the last.","index":81,"end_time":180.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":179.52,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I would have done it this weekend would have been with it.","index":82,"end_time":182.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":180.48,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"With the Christmas decoration.","index":83,"end_time":183.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":182.52,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Would have go up this weekend.","index":84,"end_time":184.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":183.48,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"But my West Manner, let''s do it a little bit earlier last weekend, everything went up.","index":85,"end_time":189.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":184.64,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And so it''s nice.","index":86,"end_time":192.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":189.99,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It is nice to have Christmas decorations.","index":87,"end_time":194.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":192.19,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So good.","index":88,"end_time":195.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":194.59,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"What can you do?","index":89,"end_time":196.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":195.87,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Anyways, so it''s the last one before the new year.","index":90,"end_time":200.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":196.63,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yes, it is.","index":91,"end_time":201.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":200.79,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s crazy.","index":92,"end_time":202.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":201.71,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I had another client meeting this morning.","index":93,"end_time":203.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":202.27,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s just wrapping up the year.","index":94,"end_time":205.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":203.59,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s wild.","index":95,"end_time":205.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":205.11,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So can you see my screen?","index":96,"end_time":208.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":205.75,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I think I''m already sure.","index":97,"end_time":209.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":208.39,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Okay, great.","index":98,"end_time":210.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":209.43,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Just to start off with the free assessment, I know I sent you the design link.","index":99,"end_time":214.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":211.03,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Did you have any feedback on that?","index":100,"end_time":215.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":214.15,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Nope.","index":101,"end_time":216.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":215.67,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It''s good to go.","index":102,"end_time":216.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":216.07,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Okay.","index":103,"end_time":217.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":217.17,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And I think I might have had one.","index":104,"end_time":219.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":217.53,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"For some reason, I couldn''t log into the page, so it came across as.","index":105,"end_time":223.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":219.73,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"A guest I know we had recommended.","index":106,"end_time":225.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":223.01,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Or Tristan, I think originally recommended was.","index":107,"end_time":228.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":226.37,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I was on vacation a couple months ago.","index":108,"end_time":230.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":228.69,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"When she sent you these, Bailey, to remove maybe the phone box in this one.","index":109,"end_time":235.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":230.81,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Did you want to do that or do you want to leave?","index":110,"end_time":237.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":235.69,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Whatever.","index":111,"end_time":237.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":237.53,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Whatever you guys suggest.","index":112,"end_time":238.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":237.81,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I am relying on your expertise, I would say, on this one.","index":113,"end_time":243.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":239.49,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":114,"end_time":243.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":243.35,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Just trying to make it, like, super short, so maybe people would do it.","index":115,"end_time":247.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":243.59,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yes, I agree.","index":116,"end_time":248.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":247.59,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yes.","index":117,"end_time":249.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":248.95,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we can.","index":118,"end_time":250.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":249.43,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We can remove those then and.","index":119,"end_time":251.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":250.03,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, we''ll do that.","index":120,"end_time":252.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":251.83,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then we''ll get it live.","index":121,"end_time":253.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":252.67,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So that''s fantastic.","index":122,"end_time":254.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":253.71,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":123,"end_time":255.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":254.83,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"See.","index":124,"end_time":255.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":255.11,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"See what happens?","index":125,"end_time":256.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":255.43,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Like I say, it''s.","index":126,"end_time":257.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":256.55,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yes, we can only keep trying, can''t we, until exactly.","index":127,"end_time":261.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":257.99,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"You know, Exactly.","index":128,"end_time":262.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":261.51,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And then for the design options for the booth, did you have a chance to go through those?","index":129,"end_time":267.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":263.83,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I. Yeah.","index":130,"end_time":268.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":267.67,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Josh is gone, so.","index":131,"end_time":270.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":268.59,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So I looked at them and I think it was.","index":132,"end_time":273.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":270.19,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And I can''t remember which number it was.","index":133,"end_time":275.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":273.71,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I think it was the last one I. I liked, unfortunately, as I said to you, I. I thought this one was the best out of the lot, to be honest with you.","index":134,"end_time":284.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":275.79,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I do like the.","index":135,"end_time":285.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":284.91,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The.","index":136,"end_time":286.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":285.83,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I mean, I think you.","index":137,"end_time":287.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":286.99,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"You''re right.","index":138,"end_time":288.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":287.91,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"You know, you''ve taken into account the fact that wherever.","index":139,"end_time":291.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":288.43,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"If you''re standing in Front of it.","index":140,"end_time":292.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":291.67,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And that, that stool, that stand is there or a table''s there.","index":141,"end_time":296.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":292.95,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I think you are seeing the more reward.","index":142,"end_time":298.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":296.74,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"That''s where my eye was drawn was the more reward bit, which I think makes sense.","index":143,"end_time":303.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":298.58,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And I think that bit at the bottom, it''s good because you then get there and you look, you will be looking down and I, I think it''s good.","index":144,"end_time":311.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":303.78,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":145,"end_time":312.459,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":312.1,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I can say I, I, I can''t do anything without him.","index":146,"end_time":315.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":312.459,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I want him to look at this because, yeah, I''m gonna spend three grand on a booth.","index":147,"end_time":319.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":315.58,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I can''t then say, oh, we didn''t like the design.","index":148,"end_time":322.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":320.5,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Can we change it?","index":149,"end_time":323.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":322.9,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And that''s like 7, 700 or something like that.","index":150,"end_time":325.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":323.82,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So understandable.","index":151,"end_time":327.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":325.88,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I don''t want to be doing that sort of thing.","index":152,"end_time":328.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":327.16,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"But yeah, I think this is the better of the lot.","index":153,"end_time":330.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":328.56,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"All great.","index":154,"end_time":331.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":330.92,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"They''re all very good.","index":155,"end_time":332.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":331.72,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"This one stuck out as well.","index":156,"end_time":334.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":333.08,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Oh, I like, I like the bottom.","index":157,"end_time":336.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":334.56,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"The coloring.","index":158,"end_time":337.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":336.52,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I thought that was a good idea, actually.","index":159,"end_time":338.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":337.32,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yes.","index":160,"end_time":339.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":339.16,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":161,"end_time":339.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":339.56,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Kind of that, like color wash or the light wash. Yeah.","index":162,"end_time":342.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":339.84,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The director who worked on this with our designers immediately was like, do they have a table?","index":163,"end_time":347.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":342.64,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And if so, where is it?","index":164,"end_time":349.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":347.8,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So, yeah, you wanted to make sure that everything was visible if you were in front of the table, so.","index":165,"end_time":353.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":349.04,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Absolutely.","index":166,"end_time":353.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":353.32,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And I think this is, this is a good, this, this one to winner.","index":167,"end_time":357.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":353.88,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So unfortunately, until I can get, I can''t get him to do anything at the moment, so he''s on his way.","index":168,"end_time":363.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":357.62,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"He''s in New Zealand for a couple of weeks, so.","index":169,"end_time":365.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":363.46,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Oh, wow.","index":170,"end_time":366.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":365.54,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":171,"end_time":366.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":366.42,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So he''s not going to be looking at anything unless it''s like, client urgent.","index":172,"end_time":370.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":366.86,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"He just won''t look at this sort of stuff, you know, so.","index":173,"end_time":373.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":370.78,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"That makes sense.","index":174,"end_time":374.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":373.14,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":175,"end_time":374.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":374.02,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I''m very much bottom of the pile when it comes to anything.","index":176,"end_time":377.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":374.66,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"When it''s client stuff is obviously paramount, so it is what it is.","index":177,"end_time":382.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":377.7,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"But, yeah, love this.","index":178,"end_time":383.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":382.65,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I think it''s good.","index":179,"end_time":384.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":383.69,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Let me just go ahead and just get him to look at it.","index":180,"end_time":387.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":384.97,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It will be the new year, like I say.","index":181,"end_time":390.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":387.85,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I think probably second week of January before I can actually sort of get him to focus on this.","index":182,"end_time":394.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":390.57,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Okay.","index":183,"end_time":395.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":395.05,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then I think we, we should get approval and we just go for it.","index":184,"end_time":398.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":395.53,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"That sounds good.","index":185,"end_time":399.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":398.73,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":186,"end_time":399.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":399.49,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We just want to make sure there was one in there that you liked in case we need to make any edits.","index":187,"end_time":403.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":399.69,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Well, I was just thinking, I was thinking whether or not we should try to redesign the other one as well, you know, the stand one.","index":188,"end_time":415.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":404.33,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"But let''s just get this one knocked on the head first because it''s not we''re buying a brand new booth.","index":189,"end_time":420.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":415.28,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Okay.","index":190,"end_time":421.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":420.68,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And it, it just literally is a lot smaller than the other one and I want to have both.","index":191,"end_time":425.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":421.2,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So there''ll be a slight disconnect between the two in terms of overall design.","index":192,"end_time":431.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":426.6,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"The coloring will be the same apart from that bottom white one, but I don''t think it''s such a big issue.","index":193,"end_time":436.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":432.12,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I think when the time comes and you know, we want to think about it, at least we.","index":194,"end_time":442.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":437.27,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We''ve got a fairly good thing.","index":195,"end_time":443.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":442.07,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We might just then do the redesign for the other one, but not for now.","index":196,"end_time":448.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":443.39,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, that sounds good.","index":197,"end_time":450.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":449.27,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Okay.","index":198,"end_time":451.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":450.63,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, it looks good.","index":199,"end_time":452.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":451.51,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":200,"end_time":454.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":453.51,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We''ll wait to hear back from you on that then.","index":201,"end_time":456.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":454.63,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Survey Monkey is good.","index":202,"end_time":458.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":457.19,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Let''s go.","index":203,"end_time":458.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":458.55,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Do you like it?","index":204,"end_time":459.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":458.99,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Okay.","index":205,"end_time":459.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":459.51,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Love it.","index":206,"end_time":460.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":459.87,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I think it''s good.","index":207,"end_time":461.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":460.53,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"All those sort of, you know, the click ones is a lot easier to use.","index":208,"end_time":464.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":461.33,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yes, I like it a lot.","index":209,"end_time":468.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":466.53,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I''m really excited about this.","index":210,"end_time":470.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":468.77,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''ve been.","index":211,"end_time":471.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":470.53,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I was telling Bailey on or we had a meeting Monday and I, I''ve been a little frustrated with Lemlist too because I have clients that are running things on there a lot and, you know, time is of the essence.","index":212,"end_time":482.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":471.05,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Time is money.","index":213,"end_time":483.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":482.73,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So you want to get things out.","index":214,"end_time":485.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":483.37,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I''ve done a lot of research on this because I wanted to find one that was a good fit for you guys.","index":215,"end_time":489.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":485.01,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And I just feel confident in this.","index":216,"end_time":491.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":489.49,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So far, so hopeful it works that way.","index":217,"end_time":493.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":491.05,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But I''ve been working with one of our developers and everything''s uploaded and it should send to all the contacts within like a 48 hour period, which is wonderful.","index":218,"end_time":500.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":493.08,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s exactly what we want.","index":219,"end_time":502.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":501.36,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, exactly.","index":220,"end_time":503.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":502.56,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"All the results will be in here in one place and it''ll just be a, a good, good one.","index":221,"end_time":511.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":505.76,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"One stop shop for this.","index":222,"end_time":513,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":511.76,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So.","index":223,"end_time":513.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":513,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, I''m glad you like it.","index":224,"end_time":515.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":513.92,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And do you want us to go?","index":225,"end_time":517.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":515.48,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Oh, I think I had a. I had this in here.","index":226,"end_time":520,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":517.92,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But the final companies list that we''ve been working on, we went ahead and we created that entire excluded column like I told you about last week.","index":227,"end_time":528.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":520.24,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Did you want some of these companies like us to pull a list together and add it to the survey, or would you rather save this for like upcoming ABM campaigns or anything in the future?","index":228,"end_time":540.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":529.12,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Is this something that you wanted included in the survey or just keep the current list?","index":229,"end_time":544,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":540.56,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I think keep the current list for now because.","index":230,"end_time":546.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":544.32,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, honestly, because we''d have to do a little bit of work.","index":231,"end_time":548.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":546.73,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We''d have to make sure we get the right job titles.","index":232,"end_time":551.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":548.85,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"You know, there''s still a couple of duplicates in there from Firms that I sort of recognize and that might be in the existing list.","index":233,"end_time":557.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":552.01,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So.","index":234,"end_time":558.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":557.89,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Okay, let''s not stress too much about this.","index":235,"end_time":560.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":558.41,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And I still think the list comes out as, what, 600 odd firms or something like that.","index":236,"end_time":565.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":560.97,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s a good chunk.","index":237,"end_time":566.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":565.53,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":238,"end_time":567.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":567.37,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So, I mean, it''s a good, what, another 2400 contacts in total, you know, give or take.","index":239,"end_time":574.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":567.73,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So I think it''s a.","index":240,"end_time":576.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":574.82,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It''s a great number.","index":241,"end_time":577.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":576.1,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, of course, you know, we''re.","index":242,"end_time":579.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":577.62,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Because again, you know, we''re going to have.","index":243,"end_time":580.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":579.18,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We''re going to have churn as we go along, so we do want to make sure we''ve got this.","index":244,"end_time":583.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":580.3,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So.","index":245,"end_time":584.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":583.9,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, let''s not worry about this list until the new year.","index":246,"end_time":586.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":584.14,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Okay.","index":247,"end_time":587.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":587.06,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Pencil that in for one of our time just to sort of agree on job titles.","index":248,"end_time":591.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":587.54,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":249,"end_time":592.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":592.02,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then if you have the ability to.","index":250,"end_time":595.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":592.54,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"To grab names, that''d be fantastic.","index":251,"end_time":597.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":595.46,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, for sure.","index":252,"end_time":598.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":597.87,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We can enrich the list in clay once we get everything down as far as job titles.","index":253,"end_time":602.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":598.35,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":254,"end_time":602.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":602.55,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, let''s do that.","index":255,"end_time":603.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":602.91,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, don''t stress about that.","index":256,"end_time":605.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":603.59,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So I think we''re good for the survey then.","index":257,"end_time":608.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":605.55,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Do you want us to go ahead and get that scheduled?","index":258,"end_time":610.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":608.51,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I don''t think we should do it the first week of January just because everyone''s going to be like, yeah, gosh, back to life.","index":259,"end_time":617.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":611.23,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Second or third?","index":260,"end_time":619.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":618.27,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Second or third.","index":261,"end_time":620.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":619.79,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Okay.","index":262,"end_time":621.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":621.31,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The thing is, look, we.","index":263,"end_time":623.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":621.75,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"This buddy newsletter thing, I can''t.","index":264,"end_time":627.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":624.3,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I. I''ve got a chap who''s getting pulled all over the place right now who''s supposed to be doing some analysis for me.","index":265,"end_time":633.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":627.1,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I am still trying to build what a survey would look like in terms of the first five questions.","index":266,"end_time":640.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":634.54,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"There''s five questions plus data.","index":267,"end_time":644.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":641.42,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So there''s a whole bunch of questions within the.","index":268,"end_time":647.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":645.42,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"The spreadsheet that we have.","index":269,"end_time":648.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":647.5,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And it''s.","index":270,"end_time":649.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":648.58,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Those are data specific questions that we can pull.","index":271,"end_time":652.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":649.43,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And we have a good cross section of clients from industry, so I think that''s going to be as statistically valid.","index":272,"end_time":659.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":653.43,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It''s going to be.","index":273,"end_time":660.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":659.91,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"To be honest, I don''t think it''s going to be anything, you know, but I need that analysis to do that.","index":274,"end_time":666.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":660.67,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And I''m still trying to go ahead and just work out what a structure would look like in terms of what a survey report should look like.","index":275,"end_time":673.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":667.19,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And a lot of it''s just down to what Josh is trying to think about and what he''s trying to get across.","index":276,"end_time":677.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":674.55,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So there''s going to be a couple of variations in there.","index":277,"end_time":680.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":678.07,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I have a horrible feeling that we aren''t going to have anything for a newsletter unless we Create one brand new with a whole bunch of different sort of information.","index":278,"end_time":691.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":681.27,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I don''t think we''d have it.","index":279,"end_time":694.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":692.87,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So, yeah, we could potentially do just pulling from what we currently have existing and not trying to make it about the survey this month.","index":280,"end_time":703.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":694.15,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And we could do that for February if you want.","index":281,"end_time":705.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":703.03,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I know it''s just trying to get.","index":282,"end_time":707.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":706.33,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"You need to try and get some sort.","index":283,"end_time":709.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":707.93,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I think we had sort of high hopes for this, for the newsletter, but it''s just trying to find.","index":284,"end_time":716.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":709.25,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Just trying to find content that makes sense, you know, and that''s our problem is that we can''t seem to have any consensus about what goes in it.","index":285,"end_time":726.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":718.57,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And if we do, it''s almost like, oh, that''s an awful lot of work because we have to write something new and it''s like, you know, so, yeah.","index":286,"end_time":734.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":727.21,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I don''t know, say if there''s like a.","index":287,"end_time":736.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":734.73,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"A way to recap the previous year, like 2025 or highlights or something like that.","index":288,"end_time":741.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":736.53,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It could.","index":289,"end_time":742.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":742.41,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I was just thinking off the top of my hand, like, if we didn''t want to do the survey off the bat, it could be like a highlight of just some things from 2025 and what we''re looking ahead for 2026 to kind of make it like a New Year''s kind of newsletter where it doesn''t have to be super formal.","index":290,"end_time":758.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":742.93,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It can kind of just be a message out to the contacts.","index":291,"end_time":761.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":758.29,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":292,"end_time":764.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":764.29,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Something to kind of like set the tone.","index":293,"end_time":766.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":764.69,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We.","index":294,"end_time":767.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":766.93,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"What we saw happen in 2026.","index":295,"end_time":769.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":767.41,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"That sort of thing.","index":296,"end_time":770.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":769.57,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":297,"end_time":771.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":770.61,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Kind of like what were your.","index":298,"end_time":772.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":771.05,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Like how the bottom part is like your insights.","index":299,"end_time":774.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":772.61,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It could just be the whole newsletter could be about that instead.","index":300,"end_time":778.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":774.77,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Or like, what did we notice in 2025?","index":301,"end_time":780.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":778.25,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"What are we looking forward to in 2026 and kind of just make it like a recap thing for the new year.","index":302,"end_time":786.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":780.21,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then in February, we can kick back off with the survey.","index":303,"end_time":790,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":786.61,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I like that idea.","index":304,"end_time":792.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":791.12,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And we can even tease the survey insights again at the bottom of that January one to talk about how that''ll come up.","index":305,"end_time":798.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":792.48,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":306,"end_time":799.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":799.2,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So if you want to put together a couple thoughts there, then we can pull that together, if that''s something you''re interested in.","index":307,"end_time":805.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":800,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, I like that idea a lot, actually.","index":308,"end_time":807.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":805.92,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Great.","index":309,"end_time":808.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":808.48,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, every.","index":310,"end_time":811.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":809.44,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Everything''s going on right now.","index":311,"end_time":812.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":811.8,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Like, the recaps.","index":312,"end_time":813.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":812.84,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Like, I don''t know if you have Spotify, but the Spotify wrapped and you could even do a play on that because what we''re using now, like Fireflies.","index":313,"end_time":820.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":813.64,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":314,"end_time":821.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":821.02,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I got an email yesterday from Fireflies, and it was like, you''re.","index":315,"end_time":824.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":821.38,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"You''re Wrapped.","index":316,"end_time":825.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":824.58,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And I was like, oh, really?","index":317,"end_time":827.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":825.82,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It literally told me you spent 74,100 and whatever minutes in meetings.","index":318,"end_time":833.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":828.3,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And it said, that''s watching the Office 760 times.","index":319,"end_time":837.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":833.98,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That''s crazy.","index":320,"end_time":839.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":838.14,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It was funny.","index":321,"end_time":839.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":839.1,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So you could even do a play on something like that.","index":322,"end_time":842.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":839.9,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Like.","index":323,"end_time":842.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":842.02,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, are you wrapped something kind of light hearted?","index":324,"end_time":846.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":842.87,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Because people like to see that.","index":325,"end_time":847.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":846.71,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Like when I. I would never open like marketing emails like that, but I.","index":326,"end_time":851.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":847.79,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It caught my attention.","index":327,"end_time":852.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":851.31,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I was like, that''s pretty funny.","index":328,"end_time":853.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":852.31,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I think everyone''s kind of taking that like idea and running with it, like you''re wrapped kind of thing.","index":329,"end_time":861.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":853.99,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So you could even do something funny like that.","index":330,"end_time":862.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":861.11,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Kind of change it up.","index":331,"end_time":863.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":862.83,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I like that.","index":332,"end_time":865.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":864.31,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I like that.","index":333,"end_time":865.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":865.19,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":334,"end_time":866.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":865.75,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Talking about Spotify, if you don''t mind me asking, what was your age?","index":335,"end_time":868.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":866.31,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Oh, I don''t remember.","index":336,"end_time":871.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":870.02,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I want to say it was in the 60s.","index":337,"end_time":873.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":871.62,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I kind of like holding all their music.","index":338,"end_time":875.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":873.22,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s so weird, isn''t it, how my wife was 82.","index":339,"end_time":878.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":875.7,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"That''s funny.","index":340,"end_time":880.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":879.54,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It was hilarious.","index":341,"end_time":881.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":880.66,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And then one of the chaps at work, he was.","index":342,"end_time":883.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":881.42,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"He''s like in his 20s.","index":343,"end_time":885.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":883.18,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I said.","index":344,"end_time":886.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":885.7,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"He said 72 was his age.","index":345,"end_time":889.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":886.34,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I was 54, which I was a bit surprised because I listened to an awful lot of blues music and things like that.","index":346,"end_time":896.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":890.02,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"But I guess I mixed and matched.","index":347,"end_time":898.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":896.79,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"God knows, I mean, some of the music that gets the recap.","index":348,"end_time":902.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":899.23,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yes, Listen to that.","index":349,"end_time":904.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":902.91,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, that was interesting.","index":350,"end_time":905.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":904.99,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, but it''s always a fun one, isn''t it?","index":351,"end_time":907.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":905.99,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"The age one.","index":352,"end_time":908.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":907.59,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"What age?","index":353,"end_time":908.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":908.19,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I love how it says too, like, don''t be offended, it''s just a number.","index":354,"end_time":913.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":910.27,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s true.","index":355,"end_time":914.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":913.87,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Everyone''s going, hang on.","index":356,"end_time":915.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":914.55,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"My wife was like, I can''t believe it.","index":357,"end_time":918.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":915.95,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And we did actually find some.","index":358,"end_time":919.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":918.43,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We did find out some thing.","index":359,"end_time":921.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":919.95,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"When we leave the house, we put the Alexa on and it plays like classical music for dogs.","index":360,"end_time":928.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":921.97,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It''s a calming music.","index":361,"end_time":929.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":928.33,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Oh, that''s so sweet.","index":362,"end_time":930.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":929.45,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And of course it''s on her account.","index":363,"end_time":932.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":931.25,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And so, you know, I don''t remember any of this music, you know, and it''s because it''s the dog, you know, so she''s got all these.","index":364,"end_time":938.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":932.69,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"These tracks.","index":365,"end_time":939.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":938.29,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"That is so funny.","index":366,"end_time":940.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":939.65,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I know, I love that.","index":367,"end_time":943.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":940.85,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"What the hell?","index":368,"end_time":944.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":943.41,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Okay, sounds good.","index":369,"end_time":947.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":945.57,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":370,"end_time":948.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":948.01,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I love the idea about the survey.","index":371,"end_time":949.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":948.21,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Sorry about the newsletter thing.","index":372,"end_time":951.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":950.01,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I think about that.","index":373,"end_time":952.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":951.61,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I like that a lot.","index":374,"end_time":953.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":952.69,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And yeah, I might just sort of send that around the houses, actually.","index":375,"end_time":959.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":953.53,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"See.","index":376,"end_time":959.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":959.05,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"See what people think about what happened this year, what they think was important and what happened.","index":377,"end_time":965.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":959.41,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And we might just talk a little bit about the firm itself, you know, how we grew or we might.","index":378,"end_time":969.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":965.61,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, we wrapped up 2025 was.","index":379,"end_time":974.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":971.61,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It was one of our best years, which is nice.","index":380,"end_time":976.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":974.41,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"That''s so great.","index":381,"end_time":977.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":976.41,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''m happy.","index":382,"end_time":978.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":977.37,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It was, it was a good year.","index":383,"end_time":979.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":978.01,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I mean, from a, A revenue point of view, it was a great year.","index":384,"end_time":982.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":979.21,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We hit our targets, which is good.","index":385,"end_time":984.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":982.93,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":386,"end_time":985.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":984.89,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We''ve increased rates per client, which we''ve been trying to do for a long time.","index":387,"end_time":990.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":986.09,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So, yeah, we got some interesting challenges as well, which has been good.","index":388,"end_time":995.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":992.65,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We''ve had some really interesting challenges in terms of.","index":389,"end_time":997.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":995.61,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Some of the technology has been interesting.","index":390,"end_time":1001.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":999.86,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We''re using like third parties now to help us with some connections that we never thought about doing before.","index":391,"end_time":1007.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1001.86,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We never did that.","index":392,"end_time":1008.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1007.94,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We also did everything in house, but suddenly we.","index":393,"end_time":1010.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1008.66,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"God, these people know what they''re doing.","index":394,"end_time":1011.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1010.46,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It''s cheaper to hire them to try and build it ourselves.","index":395,"end_time":1015.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1011.9,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Right.","index":396,"end_time":1016.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1015.94,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So, yeah, there''s some, there''s some interesting things, you know, we could, we could talk about.","index":397,"end_time":1019.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1016.42,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We talk about some things.","index":398,"end_time":1020.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1019.7,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I like the idea.","index":399,"end_time":1021.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1020.7,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Thank you for that.","index":400,"end_time":1022.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1021.58,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Great.","index":401,"end_time":1022.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1022.5,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"No, absolutely.","index":402,"end_time":1023.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1022.9,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''d love to come up with some new ideas for stuff like that.","index":403,"end_time":1026.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1023.86,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And like I said, people like the change up of just the regular scheduled programming, if you will.","index":404,"end_time":1031.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1026.42,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Like.","index":405,"end_time":1031.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1031.59,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s nice.","index":406,"end_time":1032.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1031.83,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Absolutely right.","index":407,"end_time":1033.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1032.35,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"No, I think that''s true.","index":408,"end_time":1033.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1033.03,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"That''s a nice one.","index":409,"end_time":1034.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1033.91,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I like it.","index":410,"end_time":1035.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1034.75,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And usually that performs the best anyway.","index":411,"end_time":1037.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1035.39,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So, yeah, brilliant.","index":412,"end_time":1038.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1037.39,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Thank you for that.","index":413,"end_time":1039.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1038.67,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, of course.","index":414,"end_time":1040.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1039.47,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":415,"end_time":1041.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1041.31,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Just pulled some organic stacks for the past year.","index":416,"end_time":1045.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1042.83,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I was curious what that looked like just now that we''re wrapping up the year.","index":417,"end_time":1047.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1045.31,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So for Josh, he got 338 new followers, which is really great, and 68 new connections.","index":418,"end_time":1054.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1047.99,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And I can send this to in the recap just in case sees it.","index":419,"end_time":1057.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1054.03,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then hydrant got some new followers too, and high engagements and reach as well.","index":420,"end_time":1062.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1058.34,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And now that we have that previous content continue to have scheduled, we should keep those numbers up at 2.","index":421,"end_time":1069.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1062.78,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But yeah, it''s good to see the increase in followership for both.","index":422,"end_time":1074.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1069.46,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But yeah, Josh had a lot of new new faces on his LinkedIn page.","index":423,"end_time":1077.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1074.18,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So which is good.","index":424,"end_time":1079.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1077.86,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Which I think that makes sense actually, to have to have that and yes.","index":425,"end_time":1084.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1079.14,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, brilliant.","index":426,"end_time":1085.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1084.53,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Fantastic.","index":427,"end_time":1086.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1085.49,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":428,"end_time":1087.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1086.85,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then just talking through the additional updates and we''re going to do brainstorming.","index":429,"end_time":1092.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1088.21,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I have a couple ideas I''ll bring, but if there''s any specifics that you guys want to discuss, a couple ideas, we can try to prepare those ahead of time.","index":430,"end_time":1099.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1092.25,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And I know we''re kind of just going to recap and see what we can do going into 2026.","index":431,"end_time":1105.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1100.53,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I would say if, if top of my Head.","index":432,"end_time":1109.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1105.97,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I would suggest you consider what you think, your expectations in terms of the relationship with Hydra.","index":433,"end_time":1118.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1110.97,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Okay.","index":434,"end_time":1120.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1119.77,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I will say that lead generation has never really been a thing.","index":435,"end_time":1127.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1121.13,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So I would wonder if you guys might want to define yourselves a little bit differently in terms of what you think you can achieve, you know, so it''s all very, well, we can say any number we like.","index":436,"end_time":1139.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1128.57,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"In terms of leads.","index":437,"end_time":1140.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1139.09,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It hasn''t ever happened.","index":438,"end_time":1141.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1140.09,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And in the four years we''ve been working with you, it has been four years.","index":439,"end_time":1145.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1141.89,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We''ve never achieved anything worthwhile from a lead generation point of view.","index":440,"end_time":1150.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1145.97,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Right.","index":441,"end_time":1150.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1150.21,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But redoing the website, building the brand, I think those are definite points you guys have had.","index":442,"end_time":1160.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1150.85,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Absolutely.","index":443,"end_time":1161.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1160.85,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I mean, you show the stats before, you know, the things that we put on LinkedIn, you know, we''ve increased followers, we''ve increased impressions, you know, we look at, from Josh''s point of view, those are really positives.","index":444,"end_time":1173.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1161.37,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So I think it''s, you know, it''s important that we probably just define what it is that we should be doing with you that''s real and realistic, you know, because again, it''s pointless making a whole bunch of numbers up that we don''t achieve and we just don''t hit a goal and becomes pointless.","index":445,"end_time":1190.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1174.19,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So that would be something I think you guys might want to think about.","index":446,"end_time":1193.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1190.82,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We''ll do this.","index":447,"end_time":1194.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1193.62,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"You know, we''ll, I think we''re very much thinking the same thing in terms of we should be using you guys for this and for this only.","index":448,"end_time":1202.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1194.3,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And I think it just probably takes a little bit of pressure off how we didn''t get any leads for these guys again this year, you know.","index":449,"end_time":1208.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1202.42,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"You know, is that really what we want to try to do?","index":450,"end_time":1211.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1209.46,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And so, you know, again, we''ve talked about content generation.","index":451,"end_time":1218.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1212.58,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"You know, that''s always a tough one.","index":452,"end_time":1220.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1218.75,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And it''s down to us.","index":453,"end_time":1221.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1220.47,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It''s not down to you.","index":454,"end_time":1222.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1221.51,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"You guys do a great job when you, when you give us the material, and I think you do a good job.","index":455,"end_time":1227.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1222.83,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We always get a bit of pushback on that one here, so.","index":456,"end_time":1232.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1228.99,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"But, you know, maybe that, maybe that''s almost like, you know, things that take time never work here, like video things.","index":457,"end_time":1242.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1233.95,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We''ve talked about it so many times.","index":458,"end_time":1243.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1242.02,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"You know, it''s a tough one.","index":459,"end_time":1245.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1243.5,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I think we''re almost like barriers to entry in many ways when it comes to net new ideas that involve us doing stuff.","index":460,"end_time":1253.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1245.78,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Right.","index":461,"end_time":1253.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1253.34,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So, you know, we, we, we, we have to be sort of realistic about those sorts of things.","index":462,"end_time":1259.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1253.82,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, but, yeah, I mean, I, I, I think we, we, I''ve certainly put some ideas Thoughts together and I''ll share those before we, we meet on the 28.","index":463,"end_time":1268.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1259.9,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I think it is.","index":464,"end_time":1268.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1268.11,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And so I think yeah, we should have a realistic type of conversation that''s.","index":465,"end_time":1275.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1269.39,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And there''s no blame.","index":466,"end_time":1276.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1275.27,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Absolutely not.","index":467,"end_time":1277.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1276.31,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We''re not going anywhere.","index":468,"end_time":1278.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1277.15,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"You know, you guys have been really good to us.","index":469,"end_time":1280.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1279.15,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We''re not going anywhere.","index":470,"end_time":1282.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1281.71,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"But I think it''s just for 2026.","index":471,"end_time":1285.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1283.79,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We want to be realistic about what we want to try and achieve.","index":472,"end_time":1288.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1285.55,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, that 100% makes sense and appreciate the transparency on that.","index":473,"end_time":1292.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1288.75,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We will definitely come prepare with some things.","index":474,"end_time":1293.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1292.15,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"As far as specific ideas, I''ve actually come up with a couple things in the past couple months and one of my other clients is.","index":475,"end_time":1299.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1294.03,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"He''s like our only contact for his company and he is extremely busy, kind of like you guys are.","index":476,"end_time":1305.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1300.38,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And we found a couple workarounds how to, how to get more content just in the small times we have with him.","index":477,"end_time":1311.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1305.9,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And so I, I''ve come up with a couple ideas that I think might be able to help us in the new year with you guys too because we know you''re busy but we want to be able to alleviate some of that work that you''re saying.","index":478,"end_time":1321.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1311.82,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Like it''s up to you guys that we can do it with having the information and expertise from you.","index":479,"end_time":1326.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1321.3,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I have a coup ideas there.","index":480,"end_time":1327.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1326.02,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"As far as leads specifically, I know we''ve worked with that with abm.","index":481,"end_time":1331.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1327.8,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We''ve been revamping our ABM process internally and we''re looking to launch that in the new year.","index":482,"end_time":1337.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1331.96,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we will all be getting up to speed on that to us strategists and account managers on that.","index":483,"end_time":1343.239,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1338.04,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But yes, we''ve been reworking that.","index":484,"end_time":1345,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1343.239,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So hopefully we can incorporate that into a new initiative or campaign.","index":485,"end_time":1348.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1345,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But I agree we, we can set a couple of those things up and talk about that, um, instead of it just kind of being an open ended thing like you were saying.","index":486,"end_time":1356.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1348.76,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So yes, I''m excited to come with a couple ideas and if anything else pops up that we can prepare ahead of time, just let us know.","index":487,"end_time":1362.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1356.27,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But I think it''ll be productive discussion.","index":488,"end_time":1364.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1362.71,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So it''s good to just have a session to throw it all out there and then we can move forward in the year.","index":489,"end_time":1369.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1364.91,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We should, we, we absolutely should.","index":490,"end_time":1371.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1370.11,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I think that''s, that''s the biggest, it''s the most productive way to, to work together is to just make sure we''re all on the same page, you know, and an expectation to, to be real.","index":491,"end_time":1380.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1371.63,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Otherwise it just becomes.","index":492,"end_time":1383.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1381.51,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Because I, I would almost say we''re ignoring the whole leads thing.","index":493,"end_time":1386.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1383.19,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Because it''s like it''s not happening.","index":494,"end_time":1387.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1386.19,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"But just focus on what we are working together on.","index":495,"end_time":1391.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1388.47,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So.","index":496,"end_time":1391.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1391.43,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yes.","index":497,"end_time":1392.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1391.99,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, but we''ll, we''ll come with some fresh ideas because we do want you to guys to get leads and, and have that success there.","index":498,"end_time":1398.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1392.47,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So, yes, I, I would say if anything else, to get, to get the web page working and to get the.","index":499,"end_time":1407.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1398.03,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Right.","index":500,"end_time":1407.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1407.52,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"If anything else, if we can go ahead and get people going, this makes sense.","index":501,"end_time":1413.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1409.04,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I don''t think this is such a burden.","index":502,"end_time":1416.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1414.8,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I''m going to go ahead and click on the button.","index":503,"end_time":1418.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1416.88,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"If I can have that sorted out, then frankly, as far as I''m concerned, it''s paid for the entire engagement.","index":504,"end_time":1426.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1419.12,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Because that to me is where it all works.","index":505,"end_time":1429.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1426.72,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Because we are sending people there all the time.","index":506,"end_time":1433.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1429.92,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We are constantly seeing people going to the contact page, the assessment page, but we''re not seeing them come back to us.","index":507,"end_time":1440.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1433.63,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And that is the biggest mystery to us.","index":508,"end_time":1443.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1440.71,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":509,"end_time":1444.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1444.23,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Because, you know, and I, and I don''t know if I mentioned this, but as soon as we go ahead and get on the phone with the client, they just think, oh, this is the best thing since sliced bread.","index":510,"end_time":1451.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1444.63,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":511,"end_time":1452.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1452.15,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Where do we sign?","index":512,"end_time":1453.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1452.51,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I have.","index":513,"end_time":1453.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1453.35,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We have never had a problem with that.","index":514,"end_time":1455.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1453.91,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"That''s worked really, really well.","index":515,"end_time":1457.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1455.59,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"But we can''t, we''re not obviously translating it particularly well.","index":516,"end_time":1461.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1457.03,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I don''t know why I can''t work it out.","index":517,"end_time":1464.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1461.98,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It.","index":518,"end_time":1465.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1465.1,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It is a lot of the, just the people''s attention span things because we have other clients that go through this too and it''s, it''s the same thing where once they get on the call or get to the point where they need to like, oh, this is great.","index":519,"end_time":1476.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1465.5,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And it''s, it''s just getting them in, it''s getting to fill out the form and things like that.","index":520,"end_time":1481.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1476.82,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So.","index":521,"end_time":1482.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1481.66,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But I would say that''s our, that''s our goal.","index":522,"end_time":1484.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1482.46,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We need to get that sorted out.","index":523,"end_time":1486.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1484.7,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"If there was any one thing that we wanted to pivot on success, that is it.","index":524,"end_time":1490.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1486.38,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":525,"end_time":1491.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1490.8,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Getting someone to go, I got your email or I went on your website.","index":526,"end_time":1495.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1491.44,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I''m interested in what you have to say.","index":527,"end_time":1497.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1496.08,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I filled in a form or I gave you guys a call or I dropped you an email.","index":528,"end_time":1501.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1497.68,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s important.","index":529,"end_time":1504.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1502.96,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":530,"end_time":1505.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1504.72,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Cool.","index":531,"end_time":1506.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1505.68,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s good to know, though.","index":532,"end_time":1507.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1506.12,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Okay, perfect.","index":533,"end_time":1509,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1507.52,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Brilliant.","index":534,"end_time":1509.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1509,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Well, listen, thank you for everything, obviously, and give my best to Bailey and thanks to everyone on the team for helping us this year.","index":535,"end_time":1517.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1509.48,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It''s been, I think it''s been good.","index":536,"end_time":1519.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1517.96,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Like I said, I think the content''s been good.","index":537,"end_time":1520.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1519.08,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I think we''ve beginning some great things out the door.","index":538,"end_time":1523.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1521.32,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So let''s just take the next stage we can next year and see if we can get people, you know, picking up the phone to them.","index":539,"end_time":1531.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1524.2,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Absolutely.","index":540,"end_time":1532.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1532.2,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That sounds great.","index":541,"end_time":1533.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1532.92,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Well, I hope you have a great Christmas and New Year''s and we''ll catch up in the new year.","index":542,"end_time":1537.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1533.64,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Absolutely.","index":543,"end_time":1538.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1537.8,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"You as well.","index":544,"end_time":1539.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1538.48,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And let the dog skin on.","index":545,"end_time":1542.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1539.64,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yes.","index":546,"end_time":1543.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1542.74,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I need to start playing them classical music.","index":547,"end_time":1545.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1543.38,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That''s a great idea.","index":548,"end_time":1546.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1545.06,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Brilliant.","index":549,"end_time":1547.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1546.58,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Like I say, I can''t remember what it''s called.","index":550,"end_time":1548.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1547.02,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Samantha.","index":551,"end_time":1549.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1548.74,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Sam just did.","index":552,"end_time":1550.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1549.42,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I think what she says, like.","index":553,"end_time":1551.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1550.18,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I think it''s like classical music.","index":554,"end_time":1552.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1551.54,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Like classical music for dogs.","index":555,"end_time":1554.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1552.9,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I. I''m sure that''s what it is.","index":556,"end_time":1556.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1554.78,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"You''ll find something.","index":557,"end_time":1556.979,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1556.1,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"But.","index":558,"end_time":1557.259,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1556.979,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":559,"end_time":1557.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1557.259,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And then when you leave, it will just play it.","index":560,"end_time":1560.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1557.5,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"The only thing is, is that if the dog barks with our system, it sort of interrupts it.","index":561,"end_time":1566.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1560.54,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Oh, right, right.","index":562,"end_time":1567.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1566.78,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s a bit weird.","index":563,"end_time":1568.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1567.38,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We can''t work out how to sort that problem out.","index":564,"end_time":1570.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1568.22,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"But anyway.","index":565,"end_time":1571.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1570.34,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":566,"end_time":1574.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1573.58,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Well, have a good rest.","index":567,"end_time":1574.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1574.06,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"You as well.","index":568,"end_time":1576.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1575.74,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Bye.","index":569,"end_time":1577.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1576.86,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"}],"dateString":"2025-12-17T20:00:00.000Z","host_email":"taylor.doerbaum@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/87549285494?pwd=ibWG4xRLddaHqf8JzJ7T48gg886wbu.1","participants":["josh@hydrian.com,baylee.gunnell@marketersindemand.com,michael.jones@hydrian.com,taylor.doerbaum@marketersindemand.com","josh@hydrian.com","baylee.gunnell@marketersindemand.com","michael.jones@hydrian.com"],"transcript_url":"https://app.fireflies.ai/view/01KCHTRXDD3A0AV6C2FG7Z6KJH","organizer_email":"taylor.doerbaum@marketersindemand.com"}'::jsonb,
    '{"label":"positive","confidence":0.92,"bullets":["Agreed to launch survey campaign in second week of January after holiday downtime subsides.","Michael approved booth design option but deferred final sign-off until January due to stakeholder absence.","Team aligned on developing a lighter, recap-style January newsletter highlighting 2025 achievements.","New tool SurveyMonkey adopted; Michael confirmed it''s easier and preferred over previous platforms.","Discussed setting realistic 2026 goals, refocusing away from lead gen toward stronger website conversions."],"highlights":[{"quote":"If we can go ahead and get people going, this makes sense... it''s paid for the entire engagement.","speaker":"Michael Jones"},{"quote":"I like that idea a lot, actually.","speaker":"Michael Jones"},{"quote":"We will definitely come prepare with some things.","speaker":"Taylor Doerbaum"}],"topics":["survey","newsletter","delivery","expectations","design"],"model":"openai/gpt-4-1106-preview","version":1,"generated_at":"2025-12-19T00:00:00Z"}'::jsonb,
    '{"fireflies_summary":{"notes":"## **Survey and Lead Generation Strategy**\n\nThe team agreed to launch the survey in early January with a focus on realistic lead expectations and clearer goal setting.\n\n- **Michael Jones confirmed the survey is ready to go live and suggested scheduling it for the second or third week of January to avoid holiday distractions** (25:06)  \n    - The survey is designed to send to all contacts within **48 hours**, consolidating results in one place for efficient analysis.  \n    - Michael emphasized the need to finalize the first five questions and structure the survey report with input from Josh.  \n    - They decided to hold off on expanding the contact list now due to duplicates and job title cleanup, planning to revisit after the new year.  \n    - The goal is to focus on achievable outcomes rather than unrealistic lead generation targets.\n\n- **Michael highlighted the absence of meaningful lead generation over the past four years with Hydra, urging a redefinition of the partnership’s purpose** (18:25)  \n    - He acknowledged successes in brand building and follower growth but stressed that lead generation has never met expectations.  \n    - Michael proposed focusing on realistic deliverables, reducing pressure around leads to better align efforts.  \n    - Taylor Doerbaum responded with ideas to ease content creation burdens and planned to bring fresh lead generation strategies in 2026.  \n    - They aim to integrate revamped ABM processes into new campaigns early next year to improve lead outcomes.\n\n## **Website and Conversion Optimization**\n\nFixing the website’s contact and assessment pages is the top priority to convert visitors into clients.\n\n- **Michael emphasized that getting the website contact and assessment pages fully functional would justify the entire engagement cost** (23:18)  \n    - Visitors frequently land on these pages but fail to convert, which is the biggest mystery affecting lead flow.  \n    - Once clients reach out by phone, conversion is nearly 100%, demonstrating a strong closing process post-contact.  \n    - The team agreed that improving user flow to encourage form completions or calls is the key pivot for success.  \n    - Taylor noted that short attention spans are a common barrier, confirming this is a widespread challenge across clients.\n\n## **Content and Newsletter Planning**\n\nThe team will shift the January newsletter focus to a light, engaging yearly recap instead of survey results.\n\n- **Taylor proposed a New Year’s newsletter highlighting 2025’s key moments and 2026 outlook, inspired by popular formats like Spotify Wrapped** (11:34)  \n    - Michael liked the idea of a lighthearted recap to engage contacts without heavy formal content.  \n    - The newsletter would set the tone for the year and tease upcoming survey insights scheduled for February.  \n    - This approach addresses current content creation challenges and eases workload by repurposing existing material.  \n    - It also aligns with audience preferences for relatable, less formal communications.\n\n- **Organic growth metrics showed positive momentum, with Josh gaining 338 new followers and 68 new connections in the past year** (17:19)  \n    - Hydrant also experienced increased follower engagement and reach, supporting ongoing content scheduling.  \n    - These gains validate the brand-building efforts, even as lead generation remains a challenge.  \n    - Maintaining this momentum is important for long-term engagement and visibility.\n\n## **Exhibition Booth Design and Budget**\n\nA preferred booth design was selected with plans to finalize approval after input from a key stakeholder.\n\n- **Michael identified the last design option as the strongest and plans to get final approval from Josh in mid-January** (06:05)  \n    - The chosen design balances visibility and aesthetic, especially accounting for the presence of a table or stool in front.  \n    - The booth cost is approximately **$3,000**, and Michael wants to avoid redesign costs of around **$700** by confirming the design upfront.  \n    - They agreed to finalize this booth first before redesigning the smaller stand booth later, accepting minor design inconsistencies between the two.  \n    - This staged approach manages budget and timing risks while ensuring brand consistency.\n\n## **Partnership Expectations and Operational Realism**\n\nThe discussion revealed a need to realign expectations between the firm and Hydra, focusing on achievable goals with no blame.\n\n- **Michael stressed the importance of setting realistic goals for 2026, particularly around lead generation, based on four years of experience** (19:10)  \n    - He acknowledged Hydra’s value in website, brand, and content support but noted internal barriers to adopting new ideas like video content.  \n    - Both parties agreed to maintain the partnership without blame, emphasizing transparency and practical targets.  \n    - Taylor committed to bringing new ideas to reduce client workload and enhance content output despite busy schedules.  \n    - Michael reinforced that clear expectations and honest conversations are the most productive way to work together going forward.\n\n- **Michael plans to share additional thoughts before the next meeting on December 28 to shape the 2026 strategy** (21:28)  \n    - The upcoming session aims to align all stakeholders on priorities and actionable plans.  \n    - This collaborative approach intends to improve clarity and focus throughout the year.  \n    - The team will prepare ideas and identify any additional discussion points ahead of time.","outline":null,"keywords":["Survey Launch","Booth Design","Lead Generation","Newsletter Strategy","Website Conversion","Content Creation"],"overview":"- **Survey Launch Planned:** Survey to go live in early January, focusing on realistic lead expectations and achievable goals.  \n- **Website Optimization Priority:** Fixing website contact and assessment pages is crucial for converting visitors into clients.  \n- **Newsletter Focus Shift:** January newsletter will provide a light recap of past year instead of survey results, easing content creation.  \n- **Booth Design Finalized:** Preferred booth design chosen, aiming for final approval by mid-January to manage costs and branding.  \n- **Realistic Partnership Goals:** Emphasis on setting achievable targets for 2026, maintaining a blame-free, transparent partnership approach.  \n- **Ongoing Engagement Metrics:** Positive growth noted with 338 new followers and 68 new connections, supporting brand-building efforts.","action_items":"\n**Michael Jones**\nSend design feedback and final approval for the booth to designer post-New Year, after consulting Josh (06:05)\nShare ideas and thoughts on realistic marketing goals and content before the 28th December meeting (20:50)\nEnsure website contact and assessment page is functioning optimally to convert visitors into clients, emphasize its priority (23:00)\n\n**Taylor Doerbaum**\nRemove phone box from free assessment as approved and launch it live (04:00)\nSchedule the survey to launch the second or third week of January (10:18)\nHold on expanding company list for survey until new year; plan to clean and enrich the list then (09:47)\nPrepare and propose a New Year''s themed newsletter for January as a 2025 recap and 2026 preview with a teaser for February’s survey insights (11:30)\nDevelop content gathering workarounds to ease client burden on content creation (21:30)\nPrepare for brainstorming session on 28th December with tailored ideas for marketing and lead generation strategy adjustments (22:36)\n\n**Unassigned**\nContinue scheduling and running the ABM process revamp to integrate new leads generation strategies (21:30)\n"},"migrated_from":"contract_meetings","original_id":"b98bc594-4700-42f8-b589-5475a909f515","master_marketer":{"status":"migrated"}}'::jsonb,
